#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:1
msgid "Find Your Way Around"
msgstr "Tafuta Njia Yako Karibu"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:3
msgid ""
"This section describes the different pages that you are going to see as you "
"navigate around the NMHS Content Management System Admin interface."
msgstr ""
"Sehemu hii inafafanua kurasa tofauti ambazo utaona unapozunguka kwenye "
"kiolesura cha Msimamizi wa Mfumo wa Kudhibiti Maudhui ya NMHS."

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:5
msgid "How to reach the Dashboard"
msgstr "Jinsi ya kufikia Dashibodi"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:7
msgid ""
"The ClimWeb login button can be found at the top left corner of the website."
msgstr ""
"Kitufe cha kuingia cha ClimWeb kinaweza kupatikana kwenye kona ya juu "
"kushoto ya tovuti."

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:9
msgid ""
"![Access Dashboard](../_static/images/navigating/access_dashboard_1.png "
"\"Access Dashboard\")"
msgstr ""
"![Fikia Dashibodi](../_static/images/navigating/access_dashboard_1.png "
"\"Access Dashboard\")"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:9
msgid "Access Dashboard"
msgstr "Fikia Dashibodi"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:11
msgid ""
"Logging into the ClimWeb automatically takes you to the Dashboard. If you "
"navigate away from the dashboard, you can return to it at any time by "
"clicking on the NMHS logo in the top-left section of your screen."
msgstr ""
"Kuingia kwenye ClimWeb hukupeleka kiotomatiki kwenye Dashibodi. Ukitoka "
"kwenye dashibodi, unaweza kurejea kwake wakati wowote kwa kubofya nembo ya "
"NMHS katika sehemu ya juu kushoto ya skrini yako."

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:14
msgid "The Dashboard"
msgstr "Dashibodi"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:16
msgid ""
"The Dashboard is the main hub of the website. From the dashboard, you can "
"access all of the content you create in the ClimWeb as well as reports, "
"settings, and other content management features."
msgstr ""
"Dashibodi ndio kitovu kikuu cha tovuti. Kutoka kwenye dashibodi, unaweza "
"kufikia maudhui yote unayounda katika ClimWeb pamoja na ripoti, mipangilio, "
"na vipengele vingine vya udhibiti wa maudhui."

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:18
msgid "![Dashboard](../_static/images/navigating/Dashboard_1.png \"Dashboard\")"
msgstr "![Dashibodi](../_static/images/navigating/Dashboard_1.png \"Dashibodi\")"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:18
msgid "Dashboard"
msgstr "Dashibodi"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:20
msgid ""
"What you see in your Dashboard depends on your user role. Common user roles "
"include editors, moderators, composers, approvers, forecasters and "
"administrators."
msgstr ""
"Unachokiona kwenye Dashibodi yako kinategemea jukumu lako la mtumiaji. "
"Majukumu ya kawaida ya mtumiaji ni pamoja na wahariri, wasimamizi, watunzi, "
"waidhinishaji, watabiri na wasimamizi."

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:23
msgid ""
"The following are some of the tools that you can find within the Dashboard:"
msgstr "Zifuatazo ni baadhi ya zana ambazo unaweza kupata ndani ya Dashibodi:"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:25
msgid "The Dashboard Panels"
msgstr "Paneli za Dashibodi"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:27
msgid ""
"The dashboard panels provide you with an overview of the various states of "
"your pages."
msgstr ""
"Paneli za dashibodi hukupa muhtasari wa hali mbalimbali za kurasa zako."

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:29
msgid "The different panels on your dashboard are as follows:"
msgstr "Paneli tofauti kwenye dashibodi yako ni kama ifuatavyo:"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:31
msgid "**1. Your pages in a workflow**"
msgstr "**1. Kurasa zako katika mtiririko wa kazi**"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:33
msgid ""
"The Your pages in a workflow panel shows you any pages in moderation that "
"you own or have submitted for moderation yourself. It also shows the "
"moderation tasks that are pending and how long the tasks have been open."
msgstr ""
"Kurasa zako katika kidirisha cha mtiririko wa kazi hukuonyesha kurasa zozote"
" katika udhibiti ambazo unamiliki au umewasilisha kwa udhibiti mwenyewe. Pia"
" inaonyesha kazi za udhibiti ambazo zinasubiri na ni muda gani kazi "
"zimefunguliwa."

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:35
msgid "**2. Awaiting your review**"
msgstr "**2. Inasubiri ukaguzi wako**"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:37
msgid ""
"If your webmaster or web developer gives you permission to perform "
"moderation actions, your Wagtail dashboard displays the Awaiting your review"
" panel. This panel shows content that's ready for you to review."
msgstr ""
"Iwapo msimamizi wako wa tovuti au msanidi programu atakupa ruhusa ya kufanya"
" vitendo vya udhibiti, dashibodi yako ya Wagtail itaonyesha Paneli yako ya "
"Kusubiri ukaguzi. Paneli hii inaonyesha maudhui ambayo yako tayari kwako "
"kukagua."

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:39
msgid "From the panel, you can perform the following actions:"
msgstr "Kutoka kwa paneli, unaweza kufanya vitendo vifuatavyo:"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:41
msgid ""
"Click the name of a page to edit that page. Use the buttons to move the page"
" to the next stage in your workflow by requesting changes to a page, "
"approving the page, or approving the page with a comment. Get a quick view "
"of the page status by hovering over the indicator circles to get more "
"information about the pending task. The indicator circles show a tick for a "
"completed task or an empty circle for an incomplete one. See how long a page"
" has been waiting for review. Your most recent edits The Your most recent "
"edits panel displays the five pages you last edited."
msgstr ""
"Bofya jina la ukurasa ili kuhariri ukurasa huo. Tumia vitufe kusogeza "
"ukurasa hadi hatua inayofuata katika mtiririko wako wa kazi kwa kuomba "
"mabadiliko kwenye ukurasa, kuidhinisha ukurasa, au kuidhinisha ukurasa kwa "
"maoni. Pata mwonekano wa haraka wa hali ya ukurasa kwa kuelea juu ya miduara"
" ya kiashirio ili kupata maelezo zaidi kuhusu kazi inayosubiri. Miduara ya "
"kiashirio inaonyesha tiki kwa kazi iliyokamilishwa au duara tupu kwa "
"isiyokamilika. Tazama ni muda gani ukurasa umesubiri kukaguliwa. Uhariri "
"wako wa hivi majuzi zaidi Paneli yako ya kuhariri hivi karibuni inaonyesha "
"kurasa tano ulizohariri mwisho."

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:48
msgid ""
"The panel also shows the date that you last edited the pages as well as the "
"current status of the pages."
msgstr ""
"Paneli pia inaonyesha tarehe ambayo ulihariri kurasa mara ya mwisho pamoja "
"na hali ya sasa ya kurasa."

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:50
msgid "**3. Your locked pages**"
msgstr "**3. Kurasa zako zilizofungwa**"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:52
msgid ""
"The Your locked pages panel shows all of the pages you've locked so that "
"only you can edit them. From this panel, you can quickly view the date you "
"locked a page. To edit a locked page, click the name."
msgstr ""
"Paneli ya Kurasa zako zilizofungwa huonyesha kurasa zote ambazo umezifunga "
"ili wewe tu uweze kuzihariri. Kutoka kwa paneli hii, unaweza kutazama kwa "
"haraka tarehe uliyofunga ukurasa. Ili kuhariri ukurasa uliofungwa, bofya "
"jina."

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:55
msgid "The Sidebar"
msgstr "Upau wa kando"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:57
msgid ""
"On the left-hand side of the dashboard and throughout the ClimWeb is a menu "
"called the Sidebar. You can use the Sidebar to navigate to different parts "
"of the ClimWeb."
msgstr ""
"Upande wa kushoto wa dashibodi na kote kwenye ClimWeb kuna menyu inayoitwa "
"Upau wa kando. Unaweza kutumia Upau wa kando kuelekea sehemu tofauti za "
"ClimWeb."

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:59
msgid ""
"The Sidebar helps you quickly access your content as well as ClimWeb "
"features and settings. The items on the Sidebar can vary depending on what "
"you have access to. These features include Search, Documents, Snippets, "
"Forms, Reports, Settings, and Help."
msgstr ""
"Upau wa kando hukusaidia kufikia maudhui yako kwa haraka na vipengele na "
"mipangilio ya ClimWeb. Vipengee vilivyo kwenye Upau wa Kando vinaweza "
"kutofautiana kulingana na kile unachoweza kufikia. Vipengele hivi ni pamoja "
"na Utafutaji, Hati, Vijisehemu, Fomu, Ripoti, Mipangilio na Usaidizi."

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:61
msgid ""
"If you want the Sidebar to take up less space, you can click the white arrow"
" near the top of the Sidebar to switch it into slim mode and give yourself "
"more space for writing."
msgstr ""
"Iwapo ungependa Upau wa kando uchukue nafasi kidogo, unaweza kubofya kishale"
" cheupe karibu na sehemu ya juu ya Upau wa kando ili kuubadilisha kuwa hali "
"nyembamba na ujipe nafasi zaidi ya kuandika."

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:64
msgid "The Explorer Page"
msgstr "Ukurasa wa Explorer"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:66
msgid ""
"The Explorer page allows you to view a page’s children and perform actions "
"on them. On the Explorer page, you can publish and unpublish pages. You can "
"also move the pages to other sections, drill down into the content tree, or "
"reorder child pages within a parent."
msgstr ""
"Ukurasa wa Kivinjari hukuruhusu kutazama watoto wa ukurasa na kufanya "
"vitendo juu yao. Kwenye ukurasa wa Explorer, unaweza kuchapisha na "
"kubatilisha uchapishaji wa kurasa. Unaweza pia kuhamisha kurasa hadi sehemu "
"zingine, kuchimba chini kwenye mti wa maudhui, au kupanga upya kurasa za "
"watoto ndani ya mzazi."

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:68
msgid ""
"You can see the name of the page whose Explorer page you are on as a heading"
" at the top of the screen. If the page has child pages within it, then you "
"can see a list displaying the child pages below the heading. Clicking the "
"title of a child page takes you to the edit screen, from which you can edit "
"that child page."
msgstr ""
"Unaweza kuona jina la ukurasa ambao ukurasa wa Kivinjari uko kama kichwa juu"
" ya skrini. Ikiwa ukurasa una kurasa za watoto ndani yake, basi unaweza "
"kuona orodha inayoonyesha kurasa za watoto chini ya kichwa. Kubofya kichwa "
"cha ukurasa wa mtoto kunakupeleka kwenye skrini ya kuhariri, ambayo unaweza "
"kuhariri ukurasa huo wa mtoto."

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:70
msgid ""
"If you hover over a child page, you get an arrow on the right-hand side of "
"that child page row. Clicking the arrow displays a further level of child "
"pages."
msgstr ""
"Ukielea juu ya ukurasa wa mtoto, unapata mshale upande wa kulia wa safu hiyo"
" ya ukurasa wa mtoto. Kubofya mshale huonyesha kiwango zaidi cha kurasa za "
"watoto."

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:72
msgid "![Explorer](../_static/images/navigating/Explorer_page_1.png \"Explorer\")"
msgstr ""
"![Explorer](../_static/images/navigating/Explorer_page_1.png \"Explorer\")"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:72
msgid "Explorer"
msgstr "Mchunguzi"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:74
msgid ""
"Additionally, hovering over a child page displays a checkbox at the left-"
"hand side of the child page row. Selecting one or more child pages by "
"clicking their checkboxes gives you an action bar at the bottom of the "
"Explorer page. Clicking on any of the options in the action bar takes you to"
" a confirmation page from which you can confirm the action."
msgstr ""
"Zaidi ya hayo, kuelea juu ya ukurasa wa mtoto huonyesha kisanduku cha kuteua"
" katika upande wa kushoto wa safu mlalo ya ukurasa wa mtoto. Kuchagua "
"ukurasa wa mtoto mmoja au zaidi kwa kubofya visanduku vya kuteua hukupa upau"
" wa kitendo chini ya ukurasa wa Kichunguzi. Kubofya chaguo lolote katika "
"upau wa kitendo kunakupeleka kwenye ukurasa wa uthibitishaji ambapo unaweza "
"kuthibitisha kitendo."

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:76
msgid ""
"![Child pages](../_static/images/navigating/child_pages.png \"Child pages\")"
msgstr ""
"![Kurasa za watoto](../_static/images/navigating/child_pages.png \"Kurasa za"
" watoto\")"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:76
msgid "Child pages"
msgstr "Kurasa za watoto"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:78
msgid ""
"As you drill down through the site, the breadcrumb (the row of pages "
"beginning with the home icon) displays the path you have taken. Clicking on "
"the page titles in the breadcrumb takes you to the Explorer screen for that "
"page."
msgstr ""
"Unapochimba chini kwenye tovuti, mkatetaka (safu ya kurasa zinazoanza na "
"ikoni ya nyumbani) huonyesha njia ambayo umechukua. Kubofya kwenye mada za "
"ukurasa kwenye mkatetaka kukupeleka kwenye skrini ya Kivinjari kwa ukurasa "
"huo."

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:80
msgid "![Breadcrumb](../_static/images/navigating/breadcrumb.png \"Breadcrumb\")"
msgstr "![Breadcrumb](../_static/images/navigating/breadcrumb.png \"Breadcrumb\")"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:80
msgid "Breadcrumb"
msgstr "Breadcrumb"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:82
msgid ""
"Clicking on the … Actions dropdown shows a list of actions for the parent "
"page, like Move, Copy, Delete, Unpublish, and History. Also, clicking the "
"Sort menu order option from the dropdown takes you to the ordering page."
msgstr ""
"Kubofya kwenye ... menyu kunjuzi ya Vitendo inaonyesha orodha ya vitendo kwa"
" ukurasa mzazi, kama vile Hamisha, Nakili, Futa, Batilisha Uchapishaji na "
"Historia. Pia, kubofya chaguo la menyu ya Panga kutoka kwenye menyu kunjuzi "
"hukupeleka kwenye ukurasa wa kuagiza."

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:84
msgid "![Actions](../_static/images/navigating/actions_page.png \"Actions\")"
msgstr "![Actions](../_static/images/navigating/actions_page.png \"Actions\")"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:84
msgid "Actions"
msgstr "Vitendo"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:87
msgid "Search the ClimWeb"
msgstr "Tafuta ClimWeb"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:89
msgid ""
"The search feature is the topmost feature in the Sidebar. You can use the "
"search feature to quickly search for content in the ClimWeb."
msgstr ""
"Kipengele cha utafutaji ndicho kipengele cha juu kabisa kwenye Upau wa "
"kando. Unaweza kutumia kipengele cha utafutaji kutafuta haraka maudhui "
"kwenye ClimWeb."

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:91
msgid "![Search](../_static/images/navigating/search.png \"Search\")"
msgstr "![Tafuta](../_static/images/navigating/search.png \"Tafuta\")"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:91
msgid "Search"
msgstr "Tafuta"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:1
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)"
msgstr "Maswali Yanayoulizwa Mara Kwa Mara (FAQs)"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:3
msgid "**1. What technologies is the ClimWeb Built on?**"
msgstr "**1. ClimWeb Imejengwa kwa teknolojia gani?**"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:5
msgid ""
"The ClimWeb, along with its various components, is **completely open-"
"source** and developed on the [WMO RAF GitHub "
"account](https://github.com/orgs/wmo-raf). This implies that the institution"
" will have **unrestricted access to the source code**, allowing them to "
"identify and report any bugs, request new features, and even actively "
"contribute to the development of the codebase. This open approach encourages"
" collaboration and fosters a sense of ownership and involvement within the "
"institution."
msgstr ""
"ClimWeb, pamoja na vipengee vyake mbalimbali, ni **chanzo huria** na "
"imeundwa kwenye [akaunti ya WMO RAF GitHub](https://github.com/orgs/wmo-"
"raf). Hii ina maana kwamba taasisi itakuwa na **ufikiaji usio na kikomo wa "
"msimbo wa chanzo**, unaowaruhusu kutambua na kuripoti hitilafu zozote, "
"kuomba vipengele vipya, na hata kuchangia kikamilifu katika uundaji wa "
"msingi wa msimbo. Mbinu hii ya wazi inahimiza ushirikiano na kukuza hisia ya"
" umiliki na ushiriki ndani ya taasisi."

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:7
msgid "**2. Who will manage the ClimWeb Content?**"
msgstr "**2. Nani atasimamia Maudhui ya ClimWeb?**"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:9
msgid ""
"The **NMHS installing the ClimWeb and its components will be fully "
"responsible** for inputting and managing the content that goes into the "
"ClimWeb, from their side. This means that they take the instance of the code"
" and run it, without anyone else having access to the operational instance, "
"unless authorized to do so."
msgstr ""
"**NMHS inayosakinisha ClimWeb na vijenzi vyake itawajibika kikamilifu** kwa "
"kuingiza na kudhibiti maudhui yanayoingia kwenye ClimWeb, kutoka upande wao."
" Hii ina maana kwamba wanachukua mfano wa msimbo na kuiendesha, bila mtu "
"mwingine yeyote kupata mfano wa utendakazi, isipokuwa ameidhinishwa kufanya "
"hivyo."

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:11
msgid "**3. What if an NMHS already has a website?**"
msgstr "**3. Je, ikiwa NMHS tayari ina tovuti?**"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:12
msgid ""
"In cases where an NMHS already has an existing website but is interested in "
"testing the new ClimWeb, they have the option to install and run it "
"**concurrently with their existing system** for a specific duration. This "
"allows them to thoroughly evaluate and experience the functionalities "
"offered by the new ClimWeb. Once the NMHS is satisfied and comfortable with "
"the new ClimWeb, a phased approach can be adopted to gradually transition "
"and fully migrate their website to the new ClimWeb. This ensures a smooth "
"and well-managed transition process."
msgstr ""
"Katika hali ambapo NMHS tayari ina tovuti iliyopo lakini ina nia ya kujaribu"
" ClimWeb mpya, ina chaguo la kuisakinisha na kuiendesha **sambamba na mfumo "
"wao uliopo** kwa muda mahususi. Hii inawaruhusu kutathmini kikamilifu na "
"kupata uzoefu wa utendaji unaotolewa na ClimWeb mpya. Pindi tu NMHS "
"inaporidhika na kustareheshwa na ClimWeb mpya, mbinu ya hatua kwa hatua "
"inaweza kuchukuliwa ili kubadilisha hatua kwa hatua na kuhamisha tovuti yao "
"kikamilifu hadi ClimWeb mpya. Hii inahakikisha mchakato wa mpito laini na "
"unaosimamiwa vizuri."

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:14
msgid "**4. What does ‘ClimWeb’ mean?**"
msgstr "**4. Je, ‘ClimWeb’ inamaanisha nini?**"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:15
msgid ""
"The term ‘ClimWeb’, as used in this document, refers to **all the "
"components** working together to have a running website, more especially on "
"managing the website content. Read more about the ClimWeb Key "
"functionalities https://github.com/wmo-raf/nmhs-cms/wiki"
msgstr ""
"Neno ‘ClimWeb’, kama lilivyotumiwa katika hati hii, linarejelea **vijenzi "
"vyote** vinavyofanya kazi pamoja ili kuwa na tovuti inayoendeshwa, hasa "
"katika kudhibiti maudhui ya tovuti. Soma zaidi juu ya utendaji wa Muhimu wa "
"ClimWeb https://github.com/wmo-raf/nmhs-cms/wiki"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:17
msgid "**5. What with NMHSs services that do not have IT people**"
msgstr "**5. Vipi na huduma za NMHS ambazo hazina watu wa IT**"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:18
msgid ""
"A fundamental aspect considered during the design and development phase of "
"the ClimWeb was to establish a clear and well-defined system for managing "
"content and page structure. This involved creating a **user-friendly "
"interface with a modern design and intuitive features,** aimed at providing "
"users with a seamless and enjoyable experience. The objective was to enable "
"users to easily locate content and utilize the ClimWeb **without the need "
"for specialized IT skills**."
msgstr ""
"Kipengele cha msingi kilichozingatiwa wakati wa awamu ya kubuni na maendeleo"
" ya ClimWeb ilikuwa kuanzisha mfumo wazi na uliofafanuliwa vizuri wa "
"kusimamia maudhui na muundo wa ukurasa. Hii ilihusisha kuunda **kiolesura "
"kinachofaa mtumiaji chenye muundo wa kisasa na vipengele angavu,** "
"vinavyolenga kuwapa watumiaji hali ya utumiaji iliyofumwa na ya kufurahisha."
" Lengo lilikuwa kuwezesha watumiaji kupata maudhui kwa urahisi na kutumia "
"ClimWeb **bila hitaji la ujuzi maalum wa IT**."

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:20
msgid "**6. Security risks?**"
msgstr "**6. Hatari za usalama?**"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:21
msgid ""
"The ClimWeb, which is being built using open-source technologies, benefits "
"from the advantage of having a community of developers who actively "
"contribute to enhancing its security and stability. Furthermore, the ClimWeb"
" offers robust **support for secure authentication mechanisms**, including "
"username/password authentication, integration with third-party "
"authentication systems such as OAuth, and the ability to implement custom "
"authentication backends. Additionally, the ClimWeb performs **regular "
"backups to safeguard the website's data** and enable its restoration in case"
" of data loss. The NMHS are encouraged to share **only the final products** "
"intended for the public."
msgstr ""
"ClimWeb, ambayo inajengwa kwa kutumia teknolojia huria, inanufaika kutokana "
"na manufaa ya kuwa na jumuiya ya wasanidi programu wanaochangia kikamilifu "
"katika kuimarisha usalama na uthabiti wake. Zaidi ya hayo, ClimWeb inatoa "
"**msaada thabiti wa mbinu salama za uthibitishaji**, ikiwa ni pamoja na "
"uthibitishaji wa jina la mtumiaji/nenosiri, ujumuishaji na mifumo ya "
"uthibitishaji ya watu wengine kama vile OAuth, na uwezo wa kutekeleza "
"uthibitishaji maalum wa nyuma. Zaidi ya hayo, ClimWeb hufanya **hifadhi "
"rudufu za mara kwa mara ili kulinda data ya tovuti** na kuwezesha urejeshaji"
" wake iwapo data itapotea. NMHS inahimizwa kushiriki **bidhaa za mwisho "
"pekee** zinazolengwa kwa umma."

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:24
msgid "**7. Where is it hosted?**"
msgstr "**7. Inapangishwa wapi?**"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:25
msgid ""
"The ClimWeb is deployed **at the National Meteorological and Hydrological "
"Service (NMHS) level,** utilising either **cloud-based infrastructure or on-"
"premises servers**. Please refer to the provided **server specifications** "
"for more details on the hosting environment."
msgstr ""
"ClimWeb imetumwa **katika kiwango cha Huduma ya Kitaifa ya Hali ya Hewa na "
"Hali ya Hewa (NMHS),** kwa kutumia **miundombinu inayotegemea wingu au seva "
"za majumbani**. Tafadhali rejelea **maelezo ya seva** yaliyotolewa kwa "
"maelezo zaidi kuhusu mazingira ya upangishaji."

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:27
msgid "**8. Is WMO RAF managing or handing over completely?**"
msgstr "**8. Je, WMO RAF inasimamia au kukabidhi kabisa?**"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:28
msgid ""
"The **NMHSs independently manage all components of the ClimWeb in a "
"decentralized manner** at the departmental level. The ClimWeb includes an "
"administrative role (superuser) that possesses complete privileges to access"
" all components of the system. Further information regarding users and roles"
" can be found at (https://github.com/wmo-raf/nmhs-cms/wiki/Manage-Users-and-"
"Roles). It is important to note that WMO RAF does not have involvement in "
"managing the ClimWeb, as its administration and control lie solely with the "
"NMHSs. While WMO RAF does not directly manage the ClimWeb, it does offer "
"valuable support to NMHSs by **providing training and guidance** on the "
"proper management of the ClimWeb. WMO's role is to assist NMHSs in acquiring"
" the necessary knowledge and skills to effectively handle and maintain the "
"ClimWeb. This training and guidance aim to empower NMHSs in utilizing the "
"ClimWeb to its full potential and ensuring optimal performance and "
"functionality."
msgstr ""
"**NMHS husimamia kwa kujitegemea vipengele vyote vya ClimWeb kwa njia "
"iliyogatuliwa** katika ngazi ya idara. ClimWeb inajumuisha jukumu la utawala"
" (superuser) ambalo lina haki kamili za kufikia vipengele vyote vya mfumo. "
"Maelezo zaidi kuhusu watumiaji na majukumu yanaweza kupatikana katika ( "
"https://github.com/wmo-raf/nmhs-cms/wiki/Manage-Users-and-Roles). Ni muhimu "
"kutambua kwamba WMO RAF haihusiki katika kusimamia ClimWeb, kwani usimamizi "
"na udhibiti wake unategemea NMHS pekee. Ingawa WMO RAF haidhibiti moja kwa "
"moja ClimWeb, inatoa usaidizi muhimu kwa NMHS kwa **kutoa mafunzo na "
"mwongozo** kuhusu usimamizi ufaao wa ClimWeb. Jukumu la WMO ni kusaidia NMHS"
" katika kupata maarifa na ujuzi unaohitajika ili kushughulikia na kudumisha "
"ClimWeb ipasavyo. Mafunzo na mwongozo huu unalenga kuwezesha NMHS katika "
"kutumia ClimWeb kwa uwezo wake kamili na kuhakikisha utendakazi na "
"utendakazi bora."

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:31
msgid "**9. Training and capacity building: how will it be done?**"
msgstr "**9. Mafunzo na kujenga uwezo: yatafanyika vipi?**"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:32
msgid ""
"WMO RAF will conduct training sessions for the ClimWeb, which can be "
"arranged in **either face-to-face or online formats**. Comprehensive "
"**training materials**, including user guides (https://github.com/wmo-"
"raf/nmhs-cms/wiki) and developer guides (https://github.com/wmo-raf/nmhs-"
"cms), are also available. The training sessions will be specifically "
"targeted towards designated **departmental focal points **responsible for "
"each component of the ClimWeb. This approach ensures that the training is "
"tailored to meet the specific needs and roles within the NMHS, enabling "
"efficient knowledge transfer and effective utilization of the ClimWeb."
msgstr ""
"WMO RAF itaendesha vipindi vya mafunzo kwa ClimWeb, ambavyo vinaweza "
"kupangwa katika **maumbile ya ana kwa ana au ya mtandaoni**. **Nyenzo za "
"mafunzo** za kina, ikijumuisha miongozo ya watumiaji "
"(https://github.com/wmo-raf/nmhs-cms/wiki) na miongozo ya wasanidi "
"(https://github.com/wmo-raf/nmhs-cms), zinapatikana pia. Vipindi vya mafunzo"
" vitalengwa mahususi kwa **maeneo makuu yaliyotengwa ya idara **ya "
"kuwajibika kwa kila sehemu ya ClimWeb. Mbinu hii inahakikisha kwamba mafunzo"
" yameundwa ili kukidhi mahitaji na majukumu mahususi ndani ya NMHS, "
"kuwezesha uhamishaji wa maarifa na matumizi bora ya ClimWeb."

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:34
msgid ""
"**10. What about NMHS that want to migrate their website? What provision for"
" migration?**"
msgstr ""
"**10. Vipi kuhusu NMHS wanaotaka kuhama tovuti yao? Ni utoaji gani wa "
"uhamiaji?**"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:35
msgid ""
"The migration process will commence by initially **identifying the current "
"content of the pages, as well as identifying additional pages that may be "
"relevant and determining any obsolete content**. Moreover, recommendations "
"will be provided regarding optimal practices pertaining to wording, images, "
"colors, and other related aspects. The manual migration of each page will be"
" conducted in collaboration with departmental focal points to ensure "
"efficient coordination."
msgstr ""
"Mchakato wa uhamiaji utaanza kwa **kubainisha maudhui ya sasa ya kurasa, na "
"pia kutambua kurasa za ziada ambazo zinaweza kuwa muhimu na kubainisha "
"maudhui yoyote ya kizamani**. Zaidi ya hayo, mapendekezo yatatolewa kuhusu "
"mazoea bora yanayohusiana na maneno, picha, rangi na vipengele vingine "
"vinavyohusiana. Uhamishaji wa mwongozo wa kila ukurasa utafanywa kwa "
"ushirikiano na sehemu kuu za idara ili kuhakikisha uratibu mzuri."

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:37
msgid "**11. What support will be offered by WMO RAF?**"
msgstr "**11. Je, ni msaada gani utakaotolewa na WMO RAF?**"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:38
msgid "Support on the operationalization of the ClimWeb cuts across:"
msgstr "Usaidizi juu ya utendakazi wa njia za ClimWeb kote:"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:39
msgid "Assessing Quality and interactivity of existing NMHS website"
msgstr "Kutathmini Ubora na mwingiliano wa tovuti iliyopo ya NMHS"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:40
msgid ""
"Approach and present the ClimWeb to the NMHS. Integrate suggested feedback"
msgstr ""
"Fikia na uwasilishe ClimWeb kwa NMHS. Unganisha maoni yaliyopendekezwa"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:41
msgid ""
"Identify departmental focal points for ClimWeb coordination including "
"overall ClimWeb administrator"
msgstr ""
"Tambua sehemu kuu za idara kwa uratibu wa ClimWeb ikijumuisha msimamizi wa "
"jumla wa ClimWeb"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:42
msgid "Installation and setup of ClimWeb in-premise servers/cloud servers"
msgstr "Ufungaji na usanidi wa seva za ndani za ClimWeb / seva za wingu"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:43
msgid ""
"Provision one-on-one training and capacity building to departmental focal "
"points on configuration and customization of the ClimWeb and Website"
msgstr ""
"Kutoa mafunzo ya moja kwa moja na kujenga uwezo kwa vituo vya idara juu ya "
"usanidi na ubinafsishaji wa ClimWeb na Tovuti."

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:44
msgid ""
"Provision of learning materials, documentations, and guides of the ClimWeb"
msgstr "Utoaji wa nyenzo za kujifunzia, nyaraka, na miongozo ya ClimWeb"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:45
msgid "Follow-up support in troubleshooting and resolving technical bugs"
msgstr ""
"Usaidizi wa ufuatiliaji katika utatuzi na utatuzi wa hitilafu za kiufundi"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:47
msgid ""
"This also includes the implementation of CAP Alerts, Georeferenced data "
"visualization, email marketing, events, surveys, and user analytics "
"integration."
msgstr ""
"Hii pia inajumuisha utekelezaji wa Arifa za CAP, taswira ya data "
"inayorejelewa, uuzaji wa barua pepe, matukio, tafiti, na ujumuishaji wa "
"uchanganuzi wa watumiaji."

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:49
msgid "**12. How does the ClimWeb work in low internet connectivity**"
msgstr ""
"**12. Je, ClimWeb inafanyaje kazi katika muunganisho mdogo wa mtandao**"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:50
msgid ""
"The ClimWeb is optimized for low bandwidth scenarios. This involves the "
"minimisation of the use of large images, videos or heavy media files that "
"might consume a significant amount of bandwidth. The ClimWeb also supports "
"**caching mechanisms** that can help reduce the load on the server and "
"improve the website’s performance. By enabling caching, static content can "
"be stored on the user's device, reducing the need for repeated downloads, "
"and enhancing the experience on low bandwidth connections."
msgstr ""
"ClimWeb imeboreshwa kwa hali ya chini ya kipimo data. Hii inahusisha "
"kupunguza matumizi ya picha kubwa, video au faili nzito za midia ambazo "
"zinaweza kutumia kiasi kikubwa cha kipimo data. ClimWeb pia inasaidia **njia"
" za kuweka akiba** ambazo zinaweza kusaidia kupunguza mzigo kwenye seva na "
"kuboresha utendakazi wa tovuti. Kwa kuwezesha akiba, maudhui tuli yanaweza "
"kuhifadhiwa kwenye kifaa cha mtumiaji, na hivyo kupunguza hitaji la upakuaji"
" unaorudiwa, na kuboresha matumizi kwenye miunganisho ya kipimo data cha "
"chini."

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:53
msgid ""
"**13. Geo-referenced data visualization: What data sources and formats are "
"supported?**"
msgstr ""
"**13. Taswira ya data inayorejelewa kijiografia: Ni vyanzo na miundo gani ya"
" data inayotumika?**"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:54
msgid ""
"An essential feature provided by the ClimWeb is its capability to "
"**facilitate interactive visualization of georeferenced data**. This "
"includes the ability to upload and visualize gridded data in formats such as"
" NetCDF and GeoTIFF, as well as vector data in the form of points and "
"polygons. The ClimWeb also supports the integration of CAP Alerts and "
"enables the inclusion of data from external Web Map Service (WMS) sources "
"for comprehensive data visualization."
msgstr ""
"Kipengele muhimu kinachotolewa na ClimWeb ni uwezo wake wa **kuwezesha "
"taswira shirikishi ya data iliyorejelewa**. Hii inajumuisha uwezo wa kupakia"
" na kuibua data iliyounganishwa katika miundo kama vile NetCDF na GeoTIFF, "
"pamoja na data ya vekta katika mfumo wa pointi na poligoni. ClimWeb pia "
"inasaidia ujumuishaji wa Arifa za CAP na kuwezesha ujumuishaji wa data "
"kutoka kwa vyanzo vya nje vya Huduma ya Ramani ya Wavuti (WMS) kwa taswira "
"ya data ya kina."

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:56
msgid "**14. Can they use the CAP editor alone?**"
msgstr "**14. Je, wanaweza kutumia kihariri cha CAP peke yao?**"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:57
msgid ""
"The CAP Editor has been developed to be flexible in its deployment options. "
"It can be run independently as a **standalone application**, which is "
"accessible at https://github.com/wmo-raf/cap-editor. Alternatively, it can "
"be fully **integrated into the ClimWeb**, providing seamless management of "
"CAP Alerts within the ClimWeb environment. More information about the "
"integration and usage can be found at https://github.com/wmo-raf/nmhs-"
"cms/wiki/Manage-CAP-Alerts."
msgstr ""
"Kihariri cha CAP kimetengenezwa ili kiwe rahisi katika chaguzi zake za "
"kupeleka. Inaweza kuendeshwa kwa kujitegemea kama **programu ya pekee**, "
"ambayo inapatikana katika https://github.com/wmo-raf/cap-editor. Vinginevyo,"
" inaweza kuunganishwa kikamilifu ** kwenye ClimWeb**, ikitoa usimamizi usio "
"na mshono wa Tahadhari za CAP ndani ya mazingira ya ClimWeb. Maelezo zaidi "
"kuhusu ujumuishaji na matumizi yanaweza kupatikana katika "
"https://github.com/wmo-raf/nmhs-cms/wiki/Manage-CAP-Alerts."

