#: ../../_docs/Home.md:96
msgid "**User friendly website Content Management System**"
msgstr "**Mfumo wa Kusimamia Maudhui kwenye tovuti rafiki kwa mtumiaji**"

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:98
msgid "Modern look and design, mobile friendly."
msgstr "Muonekano wa kisasa na muundo, wa kirafiki wa rununu."

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:99
msgid ""
"Adopts best practices and designs benchmarked for weather and climate "
"information dissemination for NMHSs in Africa."
msgstr ""
"Hukubali mbinu na miundo bora iliyolinganishwa kwa ajili ya usambazaji wa "
"taarifa za hali ya hewa na hali ya hewa kwa NMHS barani Afrika."

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:101
msgid "Easy to use and customise without technical skills."
msgstr "Rahisi kutumia na kubinafsisha bila ujuzi wa kiufundi."

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:102
msgid ""
"Decentralised content management. Different staff can be assigned and manage"
" different sections of the website."
msgstr ""
"Udhibiti wa maudhui uliogatuliwa. Wafanyakazi tofauti wanaweza kupewa na "
"kusimamia sehemu tofauti za tovuti."

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:103
msgid ""
"Defined content publishing workflows. Editors and moderators can be defined "
"for every section of the website."
msgstr ""
"Mitiririko ya kazi ya uchapishaji wa maudhui iliyofafanuliwa. Wahariri na "
"wasimamizi wanaweza kubainishwa kwa kila sehemu ya tovuti."

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:104
msgid "Embedding Multimedia Content - Youtube etc."
msgstr "Kupachika Maudhui ya Midia Multimedia - Youtube n.k."

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:106
msgid "**Cap Alerts Publishing**"
msgstr "**Arifa Muhimu Uchapishaji**"

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:108
msgid ""
"Modern Cap Warnings Composer with simple user friendly and mobile friendly "
"CAP alert creation and management."
msgstr ""
"Mtunzi wa Maonyo ya Kisasa ya Kisasa yenye uundaji na usimamizi rahisi wa "
"arifa za CAP zinazofaa mtumiaji na zinazofaa kwa simu ya mkononi."

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:109
msgid ""
"Moderated Publishing Workflow from CAP composer to approver, including "
"commenting and email notification support."
msgstr ""
"Mtiririko wa Kazi wa Uchapishaji unaosimamiwa kutoka kwa mtunzi wa CAP hadi "
"kwa mwidhinishaji, ikijumuisha kutoa maoni na usaidizi wa arifa za barua "
"pepe."

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:110
msgid "Conforms to CAP Version 1.2 Standards."
msgstr "Inalingana na CAP Toleo la 1.2 Viwango."

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:111
msgid ""
"Search Engine Optimisation support to increase visibility and attract "
"targeted traffic to an alert."
msgstr ""
"Usaidizi wa Uboreshaji wa Injini ya Utafutaji ili kuongeza mwonekano na "
"kuvutia trafiki inayolengwa kwa tahadhari."

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:112
msgid ""
"Support for Approval Workflow from composer to approver, including "
"commenting and email notification support."
msgstr ""
"Usaidizi wa Mtiririko wa Kazi wa Idhini kutoka kwa mtunzi hadi kwa "
"mwidhinishaji, ikijumuisha kutoa maoni na usaidizi wa arifa za barua pepe."

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:113
msgid ""
"Interoperable XML API of Alert List and Detail for integration with CAP "
"Aggregators"
msgstr ""
"API ya XML inayoingiliana ya Orodha ya Arifa na Maelezo ya kuunganishwa na "
"Vikusanyaji vya CAP"

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:114
msgid "Live CAP creation and editing preview."
msgstr "Uundaji wa moja kwa moja wa CAP na hakiki ya kuhariri."

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:115
msgid "Draw / Upload Polygon Functionality for Alert Area/Areas."
msgstr "Chora / Pakia Utendaji wa Poligoni kwa Maeneo/Maeneo ya Tahadhari."

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:116
msgid "Alert to Alert/Alerts Reference Linkage."
msgstr "Tahadhari kwa Muunganisho wa Marejeleo ya Arifa/Tahadhari."

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:118
msgid ""
"**Events registrations and Integration with Online Meeting Platforms "
"(Zoom)**"
msgstr ""
"**Usajili wa matukio na Ujumuishaji na Majukwaa ya Mikutano ya Mtandaoni "
"(Zoom)**"

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:120
msgid "Create event registration forms hosted on the website."
msgstr "Unda fomu za usajili wa matukio zinazopangishwa kwenye tovuti."

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:121
msgid ""
"Automatically send invitation emails to users as they register to events "
"from the website."
msgstr ""
"Tuma barua pepe za mwaliko kwa watumiaji kiotomatiki wanapojiandikisha kwa "
"matukio kutoka kwa tovuti."

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:122
