msgid "Allow users registering to events to also subscribe to your products."
msgstr ""
"Ruhusu watumiaji wanaojisajili kwa matukio ili pia wajisajili kwa bidhaa "
"zako."

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:125
msgid "**Interactive Georeferenced data visualisation**"
msgstr "**Taswira ya data inayoingiliana ya Georeferenced**"

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:127
msgid ""
"Upload and visualise own gridded data (forecasts, advisories, climate data "
"products) on a map."
msgstr ""
"Pakia na taswira data yako ya gridi (utabiri, ushauri, bidhaa za data ya "
"hali ya hewa) kwenye ramani."

