msgid "Upload and visualise vector data (Point, areas) on a map."
msgstr "Pakia na taswira data ya vekta (Pointi, maeneo) kwenye ramani."

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:129
msgid "Visualise own CAP alerts."
msgstr "Tazama arifa zako za CAP."

