msgid "Visualise thematic/sectorial data products interactively."
msgstr "Tazama bidhaa za data za mada/sekta kwa maingiliano."

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:131
msgid ""
"Integrate external data sources ( from Regional Centers, Global Producing "
"Centers, Satellite, Google Earth Engine etc)."
msgstr ""
"Unganisha vyanzo vya data vya nje (kutoka Vituo vya Kikanda, Vituo vya "
"Uzalishaji Ulimwenguni, Satellite, Google Earth Engine n.k)."

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:133
msgid ""
"Provide a platform to support impact based forecasts, analysis and "
"advisories."
msgstr ""
"Toa jukwaa la kusaidia utabiri kulingana na matokeo, uchambuzi na ushauri."

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:135
msgid "**Email Marketing integration and user analytics**"
msgstr "**Ujumuishaji wa Uuzaji wa barua pepe na uchanganuzi wa watumiaji**"

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:137
msgid ""
"Sign Up forms for users to subscribe to NMHSs products (using Mautic or "
"Mailchimp)."
msgstr ""
"Fomu za Jisajili ili watumiaji wajisajili kwa bidhaa za NMHSs (kwa kutumia "
"Mautic au Mailchimp)."

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:138
msgid "Analyse your email marketing users data."
msgstr "Changanua data yako ya watumiaji wa uuzaji wa barua pepe."

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:140
msgid "**Survey creation and results analysis**"
msgstr "**Uundaji wa utafiti na uchanganuzi wa matokeo**"

#: ../../_docs/Home.md:142
msgid "Create custom surveys hosted on own website."
msgstr "Unda tafiti maalum zinazopangishwa kwenye tovuti yako."

