msgstr "Maktaba ya Ramani ya Wavuti - [MapLibre GL JS](https://maplibre.org/)"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:109
msgid ""
"SVG Icon Sources - [Font Awesome](https://fontawesome.com/) , [Ocha "
"Humanitarian Icons](https://web.brand.unocha.org/svg-icon-library)"
msgstr ""
"Vyanzo vya Aikoni ya SVG - [Font Awesome](https://fontawesome.com/) , [Ikoni"
" za Kibinadamu za Ocha](https://web.brand.unocha.org/svg-icon-library)"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:114
msgid "Developing new functionality"
msgstr "Kukuza utendakazi mpya"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:116
msgid ""
"A modular approach is used when developing new functionality to be included "
"in the ClimWeb. The new functionality should be developed in isolation as a "
"Wagtail Python package and published on PyPi for installation using Pip."
msgstr ""
"Mbinu ya moduli hutumiwa wakati wa kuunda utendakazi mpya ili kujumuishwa "
"kwenye ClimWeb. Utendaji mpya unapaswa kuendelezwa kwa kutengwa kama "
"kifurushi cha Wagtail Python na kuchapishwa kwenye PyPi kwa usakinishaji kwa"
" kutumia Pip."

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:119
msgid "We follow the following steps in general:"
msgstr "Tunafuata hatua zifuatazo kwa ujumla:"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:121
msgid ""
"Explore existing packages in the Wagtail/Django community that provide "
"similar functionality."
msgstr ""
"Chunguza vifurushi vilivyopo katika jumuiya ya Wagtail/Django ambavyo "
"vinatoa utendakazi sawa."

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:123
msgid ""
"If an existing package exists and cannot be directly integrated into the "
"ClimWeb, we try to customize as much as we can on top of this package, to "
"make it interoperable. Otherwise, we use it directly"
msgstr ""
"Ikiwa kifurushi kilichopo kipo na hakiwezi kuunganishwa moja kwa moja kwenye"
" ClimWeb, tunajaribu kubinafsisha kadiri tuwezavyo juu ya kifurushi hiki, "
"ili kuifanya ishirikiane. Vinginevyo, tunaitumia moja kwa moja"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:126
msgid ""
"If we cannot find existing packages, then we develop the package from "
"scratch. The idea is to avoid reinvention of the wheel where possible."
msgstr ""
"Ikiwa hatuwezi kupata vifurushi vilivyopo, basi tunakuza kifurushi kutoka "
"mwanzo. Wazo ni kuzuia uundaji upya wa gurudumu inapowezekana."

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:129
msgid "Production Deployment"
msgstr "Usambazaji wa Uzalishaji"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:131
msgid ""
"[Docker](https://www.docker.com/) is used to containerize the different "
"components of the ClimWeb."
msgstr ""
"[Docker](https://www.docker.com/) hutumiwa kuweka vipengele tofauti vya "
"ClimWeb."

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:133
msgid "Other containers used include"
msgstr "Vyombo vingine vilivyotumika ni pamoja na"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:135
msgid ""
"[PostgreSQL](https://github.com/postgis/docker-postgis) with PostGIS "
"extension as the database"
msgstr ""
"[PostgreSQL](https://github.com/postgis/docker-postgis) iliyo na kiendelezi "
"cha PostGIS kama hifadhidata"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:137
msgid "[Nginx](https://hub.docker.com/_/nginx) as the webserver and web proxy"
msgstr ""
"[Nginx](https://hub.docker.com/_/nginx) kama seva ya wavuti na proksi ya "
"wavuti"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:139
msgid ""
"[Memcached](https://hub.docker.com/_/memcached) as the caching system for "
"web requests"
msgstr ""
"[Memcached](https://hub.docker.com/_/memcached) kama mfumo wa kuweka akiba "
"kwa maombi ya wavuti"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:141
msgid ""
"[Eclipse Mosquitto](https://hub.docker.com/_/eclipse-mosquitto) as the MQTT "
"message broker. Mainly used for CAP alerts messaging"
msgstr ""
"[Eclipse Mosquitto](https://hub.docker.com/_/eclipse-mosquitto) kama wakala "
"wa ujumbe wa MQTT. Inatumika sana kwa ujumbe wa arifa za CAP"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:144
msgid ""
"These are put into a docker compose configuration file, used to deploy the "
"project using Docker Compose."
msgstr ""
"Hizi huwekwa kwenye faili ya usanidi ya utungaji wa docker, inayotumika "
"kupeleka mradi kwa kutumia Docker Compose."

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:146
msgid ""
"An initialization repository is provided that brings together all the "
"different components into one project. This can be accessed at "
"[https://github.com/wmo-raf/nmhs-cms-init](https://github.com/wmo-raf/nmhs-"
"cms-init) . An installation guide is provided in the README file of the "
"repository."
msgstr ""
"Hifadhi ya uanzishaji imetolewa ambayo inaleta pamoja vipengele vyote "
"tofauti katika mradi mmoja. Hii inaweza kufikiwa katika "
"[https://github.com/wmo-raf/nmhs-cms-init](https://github.com/wmo-raf/nmhs-"
"cms-init) . Mwongozo wa usakinishaji umetolewa katika faili ya README ya "
"hazina."

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:150
msgid "Managing Updates"
msgstr "Kusimamia Sasisho"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:152
msgid ""
"New releases with bug fixes and feature updates are periodically published "
"on the [nmhs-cms repository releases](https://github.com/wmo-raf/nmhs-"
"cms/releases)."
msgstr ""
"Matoleo mapya yenye kurekebishwa kwa hitilafu na masasisho ya vipengele "
"huchapishwa mara kwa mara kwenye [nmhs-cms matoleo ya "
"hazina](https://github.com/wmo-raf/nmhs-cms/releases)."

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:155
msgid ""
"When there is a new release, The ClimWeb Admin interface will show a message"
" indicating that there is a new release. The Website administrator can then "
"choose to upgrade to the new version, after going through the release notes "
"that accompany every release."
msgstr ""
"Wakati kuna toleo jipya, kiolesura cha Msimamizi wa ClimWeb kitaonyesha "
"ujumbe unaoonyesha kuwa kuna toleo jipya. Kisha Msimamizi wa Tovuti anaweza "
"kuchagua kupata toleo jipya, baada ya kupitia madokezo ya toleo ambayo "
"huambatana na kila toleo."

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:159
msgid ""
"The upgrade is through a click of a button, that triggers a docker build "
"process with the new versions. Once the new version is built successfully, "
"the container is restarted with the new version effected."
msgstr ""
"Uboreshaji ni kwa kubofya kitufe, ambacho huanzisha mchakato wa kuunda "
"docker na matoleo mapya. Baada ya toleo jipya kujengwa kwa ufanisi, kontena "
"huwashwa upya na toleo jipya likitekelezwa."

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:162
msgid ""
"![ClimWeb Update Button](../_static/images/technology/upgrade_button.png "
"\"ClimWeb Upgrade Button\")"
msgstr ""
"![Kitufe cha Usasishaji cha "
"ClimWeb](../_static/images/technology/upgrade_button.png \"Kitufe cha "
"Kuboresha ClimWeb\")"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:162
msgid "ClimWeb Update Button"
msgstr "Kitufe cha Usasishaji cha ClimWeb"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:164
msgid ""
"In rare cases where the automatic build trigger fails, the system admins are"
" trained to manually perform the upgrade"
msgstr ""
"Katika hali nadra ambapo kichochezi cha uundaji kiotomatiki kinashindwa, "
"wasimamizi wa mfumo wanafunzwa kufanya uboreshaji wao wenyewe"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:166
msgid "Security in Django/Wagtail"
msgstr "Usalama katika Django/Wagtail"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:168
msgid ""
"The ClimWeb, by using Django/Wagtail, out of the box contains the following "
"security features inbuilt. More details on each feature can be found at "
"[https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/5.0/topics/security](https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/5.0/topics/security/)"
msgstr ""
"ClimWeb, kwa kutumia Django/Wagtail, nje ya kisanduku ina vipengele "
"vifuatavyo vya usalama vilivyojengwa ndani. Maelezo zaidi kuhusu kila "
"kipengele yanaweza kupatikana katika "
"[https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/5.0/topics/security](https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/5.0/topics/security/)"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:172
msgid "Cross site scripting (XSS) protection"
msgstr "Ulinzi wa uandishi wa tovuti (XSS)."

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:173
msgid "Cross site request forgery (CSRF) protection"
msgstr "Ulinzi wa ombi la kughushi tovuti (CSRF)."

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:174
msgid "SQL Injection protection"
msgstr "Ulinzi wa sindano ya SQL"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:175
msgid "Clickjacking protection"
msgstr "Ulinzi wa kubofya"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:176
msgid "SSL\\HTTPS protection settings"
msgstr "Mipangilio ya ulinzi ya SSL\\HTTPS"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:177
msgid "Host header validation"
msgstr "Uthibitishaji wa kichwa cha mwenyeji"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:178
msgid "Referrer Policy Protection"
msgstr "Ulinzi wa Sera ya Mrejeleaji"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:179
msgid "Cross-origin opener policy"
msgstr "Sera ya kufungua asilia tofauti"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:180
msgid "Session Security"
msgstr "Usalama wa Kikao"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:181
msgid "User-uploaded content protection"
msgstr "Ulinzi wa maudhui yaliyopakiwa na mtumiaji"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:183
msgid "ClimWeb Specific security features:"
msgstr "Vipengele maalum vya usalama vya ClimWeb:"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:185
msgid "Ability to change admin url periodically"
msgstr "Uwezo wa kubadilisha url ya msimamizi mara kwa mara"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:186
msgid "Daily backup mechanisms"
msgstr "Taratibu za chelezo za kila siku"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:187
msgid "Brute force login preventions"
msgstr "Vizuizi vya kuingia kwa nguvu kwa nguvu"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:188
msgid "2 Factor Authentication for administrator account"
msgstr "2 Factor Uthibitishaji kwa akaunti ya msimamizi"

