#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:1
msgid "Creating Reusable Maps and Charts (Snippets)"
msgstr "Kuunda Ramani na Chati Zinazoweza Kutumika Tena (Vijisehemu)"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:3
msgid ""
"Snippets are reusable components for maps and charts. You must first create "
"these before you can add them to a dashboard page."
msgstr ""
"Vijisehemu ni vipengele vinavyoweza kutumika tena kwa ramani na chati. "
"Lazima kwanza uunde hizi kabla ya kuziongeza kwenye ukurasa wa dashibodi."

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:5
msgid "How to Create a Map Snippet"
msgstr "Jinsi ya Kuunda Kijisehemu cha Ramani"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:7
msgid ""
"![ClimWeb Atlas](../../_static/images/atlas/access_maps.png \"ClimWeb "
"Atlas\")"
msgstr ""
"![ClimWeb Atlas](../../_static/images/atlas/access_maps.png \"ClimWeb "
"Atlas\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:9
msgid "In Admin Menu, go to **Atlas → Maps → Add Map**."
msgstr ""
"Katika Menyu ya Msimamizi, nenda kwa **Atlasi → Ramani → Ongeza Ramani**."

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:10
#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:33
msgid "Fill in the following:"
msgstr "Jaza yafuatayo:"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:12
msgid "**Title** – A short name for the map."
msgstr "**Kichwa** - Jina fupi la ramani."

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:13
msgid "**Optional Description** – Explains what the map shows."
msgstr "**Maelezo ya Hiari** - Inaeleza ramani inaonyesha nini."

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:14
msgid "**Dataset** – Choose from datasets created in **GeoManager**."
msgstr ""
"**Seti ya data** - Chagua kutoka kwa hifadhidata iliyoundwa katika "
"**GeoManager**."

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:15
msgid ""
"**Layer Type** – One per snippet (**Raster File Layer**, **Raster Tile "
"Layer**, **WMS Layer**, or **Vector Tile Layer**)."
msgstr ""
"**Aina ya Tabaka** - Moja kwa kila kijisehemu (**Safu Raster ya Faili**, "
"**Tabaka Raster ya Kigae**, **Tabaka la WMS**, au **Safu ya Kigae cha "
"Vekta**)."

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:16
msgid ""
"**Legend** – Already defined in **GeoManager** when creating the dataset "
"(not in the snippet)."
msgstr ""
"**Hadithi** - Tayari imefafanuliwa katika **GeoManager** wakati wa kuunda "
"mkusanyiko wa data (sio kwenye kijisehemu)."

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:17
#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:40
msgid ""
"**Admin Area** – Select an admin level and then click on the map to generate"
" the area description."
msgstr ""
"**Eneo la Msimamizi** - Chagua kiwango cha msimamizi kisha ubofye kwenye "
"ramani ili kutoa maelezo ya eneo."

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:18
#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:48
msgid "Save the snippet."
msgstr "Hifadhi kijisehemu."

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:20
msgid ""
"![ClimWeb Atlas](../../_static/images/atlas/create_map_snippet.png \"ClimWeb"
" Atlas\")"
msgstr ""
"![ClimWeb Atlas](../../_static/images/atlas/create_map_snippet.png \"ClimWeb"
" Atlas\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:22
#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:45
msgid ""
"![ClimWeb Atlas](../../_static/images/atlas/dashboard_aoi.png \"ClimWeb "
"Atlas\")"
msgstr ""
"![ClimWeb Atlas](../../_static/images/atlas/dashboard_aoi.png \"ClimWeb "
"Atlas\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:24
msgid "**Note:** Each snippet can only contain **one layer**."
msgstr "**Kumbuka:** Kila kijisehemu kinaweza tu kuwa na **safu moja**."

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:28
msgid "How to Create a Chart Snippet"
msgstr "Jinsi ya Kuunda Kijisehemu cha Chati"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:30
msgid ""
"![ClimWeb Atlas](../../_static/images/atlas/access_charts.png \"ClimWeb "
"Atlas\")"
msgstr ""
"![ClimWeb Atlas](../../_static/images/atlas/access_charts.png \"ClimWeb "
"Atlas\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:32
msgid "In Wagtail Admin, go to **Snippets → Dashboard Charts → Add Chart**."
msgstr ""
"Katika Wagtail Admin, nenda kwa **Vijisehemu → Chati za Dashibodi → Ongeza "
"Chati**."

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:35
msgid "**Title** – A short name for the chart."
msgstr "**Kichwa** - Jina fupi la chati."

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:36
msgid "**Optional Description** – A short explanation of the chart."
msgstr "**Maelezo ya Hiari** - Maelezo mafupi ya chati."

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:37
msgid "**Dataset** – Choose the dataset that will power the chart."
msgstr "**Seti ya data** - Chagua seti ya data ambayo itawasha chati."

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:38
msgid ""
"**Chart Type** -  available options are bar graph, column graph, line chart,"
" area chart and heatmap"
msgstr ""
"**Aina ya Chati** - chaguo zinazopatikana ni grafu ya pau, grafu ya safu "
"wima, chati ya mstari, chati ya eneo na ramani ya joto"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:39
msgid ""
"**Chart Colour** - The color that will be applied to the graph when styling "
"the data."
msgstr ""
"**Rangi ya Chati** - Rangi ambayo itatumika kwenye grafu wakati wa kuweka "
"mtindo wa data."

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:42
msgid ""
"![ClimWeb Atlas](../../_static/images/atlas/create_chart_snippet.png "
"\"ClimWeb Atlas\")"
msgstr ""
"![ClimWeb Atlas](../../_static/images/atlas/create_chart_snippet.png "
"\"ClimWeb Atlas\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:52
msgid "Block Layout Rules"
msgstr "Sheria za Muundo wa Zuia"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:54
msgid "Blocks can be arranged in any order."
msgstr "Vitalu vinaweza kupangwa kwa utaratibu wowote."

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:55
msgid ""
"**When two Map blocks or two Chart blocks appear consecutively and each has "
"a description**, the **text/title alternates sides automatically**:"
msgstr ""
"**Wakati vizuizi viwili vya Ramani au vizuizi viwili vya Chati vinaonekana "
"kwa kufuatana na kila kimoja kina maelezo**, **maandishi/kichwa "
"hubadilishana pande kiotomatiki**:"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:57
msgid "Example: First block → text on the left, map/chart on the right."
msgstr ""
"Mfano: Sehemu ya kwanza → maandishi upande wa kushoto, ramani/chati upande "
"wa kulia."

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:58
msgid "Next block → text on the right, map/chart on the left."
msgstr ""
"Sehemu inayofuata → maandishi upande wa kulia, ramani/chati upande wa "
"kushoto."

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:59
msgid "This ensures dashboards remain visually balanced and easy to read."
msgstr "Hii inahakikisha dashibodi zinaendelea kusawazishwa na rahisi kusoma."

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:61
msgid ""
"✅ With this setup, you can create rich dashboards combining **text, images, "
"tables, maps, and charts**—all styled for clarity and interactivity."
msgstr ""
"✅ Ukiwa na usanidi huu, unaweza kuunda dashibodi tajiri zinazochanganya "
"**maandishi, picha, majedwali, ramani na chati**—zote zikiwa na mtindo kwa "
"uwazi na mwingiliano."

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/FAQ.md:1
msgid "FAQs"
msgstr "Maswali Yanayoulizwa Mara kwa Mara"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/FAQ.md:3
msgid "Q: How do I reset a chart or map to its default state?"
msgstr ""
"Swali: Je, ninawezaje kuweka upya chati au ramani kuwa hali yake "
"chaguomsingi?"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/FAQ.md:4
msgid "A: Refresh the page to reset all filters and parameters."
msgstr "J: Onyesha upya ukurasa ili kuweka upya vichujio na vigezo vyote."

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/FAQ.md:6
msgid "Q: Can I download the data shown in the charts or maps?"
msgstr ""
"Swali: Je, ninaweza kupakua data iliyoonyeshwa kwenye chati au ramani?"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/FAQ.md:7
msgid ""
"A: Currently, data download functionality is not available. Contact the "
"administrator for data access."
msgstr ""
"J: Kwa sasa, utendakazi wa kupakua data haupatikani. Wasiliana na msimamizi "
"kwa ufikiaji wa data."

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/FAQ.md:9
