#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/index.md:1
msgid "Atlas | Interactive Dashboards"
msgstr "Atlasi | Dashibodi Zinazoingiliana"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/index.md:3
msgid ""
"![ClimWeb Atlas](../../_static/images/atlas/atlas_showcase_notitle.png "
"\"ClimWeb Atlas\")"
msgstr ""
"![ClimWeb Atlas](../../_static/images/atlas/atlas_showcase_notitle.png "
"\"ClimWeb Atlas\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/index.md:6
msgid ""
"The Atlas is a component of climweb that enables **modular, reusable, and "
"CMS-editable dashboards** that bring together maps, charts, warming stripes,"
" and narrative content for effective climate data storytelling. This "
"component is **linked to the geomanager/mapviewer component** within climweb"
" allowing linkage with already created datasets/layers and boundary data. It"
" features:"
msgstr ""
"Atlasi ni sehemu ya climweb inayowezesha **dashibodi za msimu, zinazoweza "
"kutumika tena na zinazoweza kuhaririwa na CMS** ambazo huleta pamoja ramani,"
" chati, mistari ya ujoto na maudhui ya simulizi kwa ajili ya usimulizi bora "
"wa data ya hali ya hewa. Kipengele hiki **kimeunganishwa na kipengee cha "
"msimamizi wa kijiografia/kitazama ramani** ndani ya climweb kinachoruhusu "
"muunganisho na seti/tabaka za data zilizoundwa tayari na data ya mipaka. Ina"
" sifa:"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/index.md:7
msgid ""
"**Interactive dashboards** built using reusable blocks for maps, charts, "
"text, images, and other components — enabling flexible and modular page "
"layouts"
msgstr ""
"**Dashibodi zinazoingiliana** zimeundwa kwa kutumia vizuizi vinavyoweza "
"kutumika tena kwa ramani, chati, maandishi, picha na vipengele vingine - "
"kuwezesha mpangilio wa kurasa unaonyumbulika na wa kawaida."

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/index.md:8
msgid ""
"**Dynamic maps** supporting raster, vector tile, and WMS layers with custom "
"symbology and legend options"
msgstr ""
"**Ramani zenye nguvu** zinazoauni raster, vigae vya vekta, na tabaka za WMS "
"zenye alama maalum na chaguzi za hadithi."

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/index.md:9
msgid ""
"**Warming stripes** for a visual summary of long-term temperature trends"
msgstr ""
"**Mistari inayoongeza joto** kwa muhtasari wa kuona wa mitindo ya muda mrefu"
" ya halijoto"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/index.md:10
msgid ""
"**Customizable charts** for time-series and comparative analysis in bar, "
"column, line or scatter plots"
msgstr ""
"**Chati zinazoweza kugeuzwa kukufaa** kwa mfululizo wa saa na uchanganuzi "
"linganishi katika upau, safu wima, mstari au viwanja vya kutawanya"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/index.md:11
msgid ""
"A **user-friendly CMS** that allows teams to manage and update dashboard "
"content independently"
msgstr ""
"**CMS inayofaa mtumiaji** inayoruhusu timu kudhibiti na kusasisha maudhui ya"
" dashibodi kwa kujitegemea"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/index.md:12
msgid "Analysis at different **admin levels**"
msgstr "Uchambuzi katika **viwango tofauti vya msimamizi**"

