#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:1
msgid "CAPComposer Features"
msgstr "Vipengele vya CAPComposer"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:3
msgid "CAP Warning Composer Features"
msgstr "Makala ya Mtunzi wa Onyo la CAP"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:5
msgid ""
"The CAPComposer tool is a solution that provides a range of functionalities "
"to support the NMHS in seamlessly issuing CAP. It has been developed with an"
" aim of increasing the adoption of CAP by NMHS in Africa."
msgstr ""
"Zana ya CAPComposer ni suluhisho ambalo hutoa utendakazi mbalimbali ili "
"kusaidia NMHS katika kutoa CAP bila mshono. Imeandaliwa kwa lengo la "
"kuongeza kupitishwa kwa CAP na NMHS barani Afrika."

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:8
msgid "![CAP Example](../../_static/images/cap/cap_example.png \"CAP Example\")"
msgstr "![Mfano wa CAP](../../_static/images/cap/cap_example.png \"CAP Mfano\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:8
msgid "CAP Example"
msgstr "Mfano wa CAP"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:10
msgid "Some of the key features of the tool include:"
msgstr "Baadhi ya vipengele muhimu vya chombo ni pamoja na:"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:13
msgid "🌟 Features"
msgstr "🌟 Vipengele"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:15
msgid ""
"Modern user-friendly composer that follows [CAP 1.2](http://docs.oasis-"
"open.org/emergency/cap/v1.2/CAP-v1.2-os.html) standard. Built on top of the "
"awesome [Wagtail CMS](https://wagtail.org)"
msgstr ""
"Mtunzi wa kisasa ambaye ni rafiki kwa mtumiaji anayefuata kiwango cha [CAP "
"1.2](http://docs.oasis-open.org/emergency/cap/v1.2/CAP-v1.2-os.html). "
"Imejengwa juu ya [Wagtail CMS] (https://wagtail.org)"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:17
msgid ""
"Preview a CAP alert as you edit. Save drafts for sharing with colleagues and"
" collaborating"
msgstr ""
"Hakiki arifa ya CAP unapohariri. Hifadhi rasimu za kushiriki na wenzako na "
"kushirikiana"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:18
msgid ""
"Inbuilt CAP validation. The page will not save if you have not input the "
"required data according to CAP standard"
msgstr ""
"Uthibitishaji wa CAP uliojengwa. Ukurasa hautahifadhi ikiwa hujaingiza data "
"inayohitajika kulingana na kiwango cha CAP"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:19
msgid ""
"User-friendly alert area map tool that allows multiple ways of constructing "
"alert geographic areas, while keeping the interface simple"
msgstr ""
"Zana ya ramani ya eneo la tahadhari ya mtumiaji ambayo inaruhusu njia nyingi"
" za kujenga maeneo ya kijiografia ya tahadhari, huku ikifanya kiolesura kuwa"
" rahisi."

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:21
msgid "Upload and use your country/territory's administrative boundaries"
msgstr "Pakia na utumie mipaka ya utawala ya nchi/eneo lako"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:22
msgid "Draw a polygon"
msgstr "Chora poligoni"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:23
msgid "Draw a circle"
msgstr "Chora mduara"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:24
msgid ""
"Selecting predefined areas that you create beforehand for common alert areas"
msgstr ""
"Kuchagua maeneo yaliyoainishwa mapema ambayo utaunda mapema kwa maeneo ya "
"kawaida ya arifa"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:25
msgid ""
"Inbuilt publishing workflow using Wagtail's powerful page model, with "
"automated emails to composers and approvers"
msgstr ""
"Mtiririko wa kazi wa uchapishaji uliojengwa kwa kutumia muundo wa ukurasa "
"wenye nguvu wa Wagtail, wenye barua pepe otomatiki kwa watunzi na "
"waidhinishaji."

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:26
msgid ""
"Collaborate with team members using inbuilt comments (similar to how you "
"could do in Word) with automated notifications. Request for changes and "
"approvals"
msgstr ""
"Shirikiana na washiriki wa timu kwa kutumia maoni yaliyojengewa ndani (sawa "
"na jinsi unavyoweza kufanya katika Word) ukitumia arifa za kiotomatiki. Ombi"
" la mabadiliko na idhini"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:28
msgid ""
"Publish realtime notifications/messages to third party integrations using "
"MQTT messaging protocol"
msgstr ""
"Chapisha arifa/ujumbe katika wakati halisi kwa miunganisho ya watu wengine "
"kwa kutumia itifaki ya ujumbe ya MQTT"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:29
msgid ""
"Predefine a list of hazards types monitored by your institution, with "
"intuitive icons from [OCHA humanitarian "
"icons](https://brand.unocha.org/d/xEPytAUjC3sH/icons#/humanitarian-icons)"
msgstr ""
"Bainisha mapema orodha ya aina za hatari zinazofuatiliwa na taasisi yako, "
"kwa aikoni angavu kutoka [ikoni za kibinadamu za "
"OCHA](https://brand.unocha.org/d/xEPytAUjC3sH/icons#/humanitarian-icons)"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:31
msgid ""
"Extendable to add your custom logic and functionality. The package provides "
"an `abstract` django model that can be inherited for customizations."
msgstr ""
"Inaweza kupanuliwa ili kuongeza mantiki na utendaji wako maalum. Kifurushi "
"hutoa kielelezo cha `abstract` cha django ambacho kinaweza kurithiwa kwa "
"ubinafsishaji."

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/Composer-and-Approver.md:1
msgid "CAP Composer and Approver Roles and Publishing Workflows"
msgstr ""
"Majukumu ya Mtunzi na Midhinishaji wa CAP na Mitiririko ya Kazi ya "
"Uchapishaji"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/Composer-and-Approver.md:3
msgid ""
"Within CAP, roles such as \"Composer\" and \"Approver\" are essential to "
"ensure the accuracy and authorization of alerts before dissemination."
msgstr ""
"Ndani ya CAP, majukumu kama vile \"Mtunzi\" na \"Midhinishaji\" ni muhimu "
"ili kuhakikisha usahihi na uidhinishaji wa arifa kabla ya usambazaji."

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/Composer-and-Approver.md:5
msgid "**CAP Composer Role:**"
msgstr "**Jukumu la Mtunzi wa CAP:**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/Composer-and-Approver.md:7
msgid ""
"A CAP Composer is responsible for creating and drafting alert messages. This"
" role involves collecting pertinent information about an incident and "
"structuring it according to the CAP format. The Composer ensures that all "
"necessary details are included to inform the public or specific agencies "
"effectively."
msgstr ""
"Mtunzi wa CAP ana jukumu la kuunda na kuandaa jumbe za tahadhari. Jukumu "
"hili linahusisha kukusanya taarifa muhimu kuhusu tukio na kupanga kulingana "
"na muundo wa CAP. Mtunzi huhakikisha kuwa maelezo yote muhimu yanajumuishwa "
"ili kufahamisha umma au mashirika mahususi ipasavyo."

