msgstr "Mikusanyiko"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Collections.md:3
msgid ""
"You can control access to specific sets of images and documents by setting "
"up collections. By default, all images and documents belong to the root "
"collection, but users with appropriate permissions can create new "
"collections from the Collections interface. Go to Settings > Collections "
"from the Wagtail Sidebar to access the Collections interface."
msgstr ""
"Unaweza kudhibiti ufikiaji wa seti mahususi za picha na hati kwa kuweka "
"mikusanyiko. Kwa chaguomsingi, picha na hati zote ni za mkusanyo wa mizizi, "
"lakini watumiaji walio na ruhusa zinazofaa wanaweza kuunda mikusanyiko mipya"
" kutoka kwa kiolesura cha Mikusanyiko. Nenda kwenye Mipangilio > Mikusanyiko"
" kutoka kwa Upau wa Kando wa Wagtail ili kufikia kiolesura cha Mikusanyiko."

