"\"Manage Documents\")"
msgstr ""
"![Dhibiti Hati](../../_static/images/documents/manage_documents.png "
"\"Dhibiti Hati\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Documents.md:5
msgid "Manage Documents"
msgstr "Dhibiti Nyaraka"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Documents.md:7
msgid ""
"Add documents by clicking Add documents at the top right of the documents "
"interface. Search for previously added documents by entering the title of "
"the document in the search bar. The results automatically update as you "
"type. You can also filter the results by Collection by selecting a "
"collection from the Collection dropdown preceding the documents list."
msgstr ""
"Ongeza hati kwa kubofya Ongeza hati kwenye sehemu ya juu ya kulia ya "
"kiolesura cha hati. Tafuta hati zilizoongezwa hapo awali kwa kuingiza kichwa"
" cha hati kwenye upau wa utaftaji. Matokeo husasishwa kiotomatiki "
"unapoandika. Unaweza pia kuchuja matokeo kwa Mkusanyiko kwa kuchagua "
"mkusanyiko kutoka kwenye menyu kunjuzi ya Mkusanyiko inayotangulia orodha ya"
" hati."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Documents.md:9
msgid ""
"![Select Documents](../../_static/images/documents/select_documents.png "
"\"Select Documents\")"
msgstr ""
"![Chagua Hati](../../_static/images/documents/select_documents.png \"Chagua "
"Hati\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Documents.md:9
msgid "Select Documents"
msgstr "Chagua Nyaraka"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Documents.md:11
msgid ""
"Select multiple documents by clicking the checkbox on the left side of each "
"document, then use the bulk actions bar at the bottom to perform an action "
"on all selected documents."
msgstr ""
"Chagua hati nyingi kwa kubofya kisanduku cha kuteua kilicho upande wa "
"kushoto wa kila hati, kisha utumie upau wa vitendo vingi chini ili "
"kutekeleza kitendo kwenye hati zote zilizochaguliwa."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Documents.md:13
msgid ""
"If you want to edit a document, click the title of the document. Doing this "
"takes you to the edit screen."
msgstr ""
"Ikiwa unataka kuhariri hati, bofya kichwa cha hati. Kufanya hivi kukupeleka "
"kwenye skrini ya kuhariri."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Documents.md:15
msgid ""
"![Edit Documents](../../_static/images/documents/edit_document.png \"Edit "
"Documents\")"
msgstr ""
"![Hariri Hati](../../_static/images/documents/edit_document.png \"Hariri "
"Hati\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Documents.md:15
msgid "Edit Documents"
msgstr "Hariri Nyaraka"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Documents.md:17
msgid ""
"When editing a document, you can replace the file associated with that "
"document record. This means you can update documents without having to "
"update the pages they're on. Changing the file changes it on all pages that "
"use the document. You can also change the collection of the document by "
"clicking on the Collection dropdown on the edit page and selecting a new "
"collection of your choice. Add or remove tags using the Tags field on the "
"edit screen. Once you are done editing a document, save your edits by "
"clicking Save at the bottom of the edit screen."
msgstr ""
"Wakati wa kuhariri hati, unaweza kubadilisha faili inayohusishwa na rekodi "
"hiyo ya hati. Hii inamaanisha kuwa unaweza kusasisha hati bila kusasisha "
"kurasa ambazo ziko. Kubadilisha faili huibadilisha kwenye kurasa zote "
"zinazotumia hati. Unaweza pia kubadilisha mkusanyiko wa hati kwa kubofya "
"menyu kunjuzi ya Mkusanyiko kwenye ukurasa wa kuhariri na kuchagua "
"mkusanyiko mpya unaopenda. Ongeza au ondoa lebo kwa kutumia sehemu ya Lebo "
"kwenye skrini ya kuhariri. Mara tu unapomaliza kuhariri hati, hifadhi "
"mabadiliko yako kwa kubofya Hifadhi chini ya skrini ya kuhariri."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Documents.md:19
msgid ""
"To completely delete a document and its record, select the document by "
"clicking the checkbox at the left-hand side of the document record row in "
"the Documents interface. Then click Delete from the action bar displayed at "
"the bottom of the Documents interface."
msgstr ""
"Ili kufuta kabisa hati na rekodi yake, chagua hati kwa kubofya kisanduku cha"
" kuteua kilicho upande wa kushoto wa safu mlalo ya rekodi ya hati katika "
"kiolesura cha Hati. Kisha ubofye Futa kutoka kwa upau wa kitendo "
"unaoonyeshwa chini ya kiolesura cha Hati."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Documents.md:21
msgid ""
"![Delete Documents](../../_static/images/documents/delete_document.png "
"\"Delete Documents\")"
msgstr ""
"![Futa Hati](../../_static/images/documents/delete_document.png \"Futa "
"Hati\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Documents.md:21
msgid "Delete Documents"
msgstr "Futa Nyaraka"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Documents.md:24
msgid ""
"You can also delete a document and its record from the edit screen when "
"editing a document by clicking Delete document at the bottom of the edit "
"screen."
msgstr ""
"Unaweza pia kufuta hati na rekodi yake kutoka kwa skrini ya kuhariri wakati "
"wa kuhariri hati kwa kubofya Futa hati chini ya skrini ya kuhariri."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Documents.md:26
msgid "Deleted documents cannot be recovered."
msgstr "Hati zilizofutwa haziwezi kurejeshwa."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Forms.md:1
msgid "Forms"
msgstr "Fomu"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Images.md:1
msgid "Images"
msgstr "Picha"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Images.md:3
msgid "Add, edit, and remove images"
msgstr "Ongeza, hariri na uondoe picha"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Images.md:5
msgid ""
"If you want to edit, add, or remove images from the Admin interface outside "
"of the individual pages, you can do so from the Images interface. To access "
"the Images interface, click Images in the Sidebar."
msgstr ""
"Ikiwa ungependa kuhariri, kuongeza, au kuondoa picha kutoka kwa kiolesura "
"cha Msimamizi nje ya kurasa mahususi, unaweza kufanya hivyo kutoka kwa "
"kiolesura cha Picha. Ili kufikia kiolesura cha Picha, bofya Picha kwenye "
"Upau wa kando."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Images.md:7
msgid ""
"![Manage Images](../../_static/images/icons_and_images/manage_images.png "
"\"Manage Images\")"
msgstr ""
"![Dhibiti Picha](../../_static/images/icons_and_images/manage_images.png "
"\"Dhibiti Picha\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Images.md:7
msgid "Manage Images"
msgstr "Dhibiti Picha"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Images.md:9
msgid ""
"It is possible to select multiple images from the Images interface at once. "
"To do this, select the checkbox on the top left of each image block, then "
"use the bulk actions bar at the bottom to perform an action on all selected "
"images."
msgstr ""
"Inawezekana kuchagua picha nyingi kutoka kwa kiolesura cha Picha mara moja. "
"Ili kufanya hivyo, chagua kisanduku cha kuteua kilicho upande wa juu kushoto"
" wa kila kizuizi cha picha, kisha utumie upau wa vitendo vingi ulio chini "
"ili kutekeleza kitendo kwenye picha zote zilizochaguliwa."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Images.md:11
msgid ""
"![Select Images](../../_static/images/icons_and_images/select_images.png "
"\"Select Images\")"
msgstr ""
"![Chagua Picha](../../_static/images/icons_and_images/select_images.png "
"\"Chagua Picha\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Images.md:11
msgid "Select Images"
msgstr "Chagua Picha"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Images.md:14
msgid ""
"Also, the ClimWeb allows you to edit the data associated with an image by "
"clicking on the image to access its edit screen. Image data includes the "
"title, the file, the collection associated with it, the associated tags, and"
" the focal area."
msgstr ""
"Pia, ClimWeb hukuruhusu kuhariri data inayohusishwa na picha kwa kubofya "
"picha ili kufikia skrini yake ya kuhariri. Data ya picha inajumuisha kichwa,"
" faili, mkusanyiko unaohusishwa nayo, lebo zinazohusiana na eneo la "
"kuzingatia."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Images.md:16
msgid ""
"Changing the image file when editing an image updates the image without "
"updating the pages on which it appears."
msgstr ""
"Kubadilisha faili ya picha wakati wa kuhariri picha kunasasisha picha bila "
"kusasisha kurasa ambazo zinaonekana."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Images.md:18
msgid ""
"![Edit Images](../../_static/images/icons_and_images/edit_image.png \"Edit "
"Images\")"
msgstr ""
"![Hariri Picha](../../_static/images/icons_and_images/edit_image.png "
"\"Hariri Picha\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Images.md:18
msgid "Edit Images"
msgstr "Hariri Picha"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Images.md:20
msgid "Changing the file will change it on all pages that use the image."
msgstr "Kubadilisha faili kutabadilisha kwenye kurasa zote zinazotumia picha."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Images.md:23
msgid "Set the focal area of an image"
msgstr "Weka eneo la kuzingatia la picha"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Images.md:25
msgid ""
"The Images interface allows you to set a focal area, which can affect how "
"your image displays to visitors on the front end. If you crop your images in"
" some way to make them fit into a specific shape, then the focal area "
"defines the centre point from which you crop the images."
msgstr ""
"Kiolesura cha Picha hukuruhusu kuweka eneo la kuzingatia, ambalo linaweza "
"kuathiri jinsi picha yako inavyoonekana kwa wageni kwenye sehemu ya mbele. "
"Ikiwa unapunguza picha zako kwa njia fulani ili kuzifanya zilingane na umbo "
"mahususi, basi eneo la kuzingatia hufafanua sehemu ya katikati ambapo "
"unapunguza picha."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Images.md:27
msgid ""
"You can set the focal area of an image by clicking the image to access its "
"edit screen. Then drag a marquee around the most significant element of the "
"image, and then click Save to save it. Once you set the focal area of an "
"image and save it, you can see the most significant element of the image on "
"the front end."
msgstr ""
"Unaweza kuweka eneo la kuzingatia la picha kwa kubofya picha ili kufikia "
"skrini yake ya kuhariri. Kisha buruta ukumbi kuzunguka kipengele muhimu "
"zaidi cha picha, kisha ubofye Hifadhi ili kuihifadhi. Mara tu unapoweka eneo"
" la kuzingatia la picha na kuihifadhi, unaweza kuona kipengele muhimu zaidi "
"cha picha kwenye mwisho wa mbele."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Images.md:29
msgid "To remove the focal area, click Remove focal area in the edit screen."
msgstr ""
"Ili kuondoa eneo la kuzingatia, bofya Ondoa eneo la kuzingatia kwenye skrini"
" ya kuhariri."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Snippets.md:1
msgid "Snippets"
msgstr "Vijisehemu"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Snippets.md:3
msgid "Using Snippets"
msgstr "Kutumia Vijisehemu"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Snippets.md:5
msgid ""
"Snippets allow you to create elements on a website once and reuse them in "
"multiple places. You only have to change something in a snippet once, and "
"the changes appear in all occurrences."
msgstr ""
"Vijisehemu hukuruhusu kuunda vipengee kwenye tovuti mara moja na kuvitumia "
"tena katika sehemu nyingi. Lazima tu ubadilishe kitu kwenye kijisehemu mara "
"moja, na mabadiliko yanaonekana katika matukio yote."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Snippets.md:7
msgid ""
"The use of snippets varies between websites. Wagtail developers use snippets"
" for the following purposes:"
msgstr ""
"Matumizi ya vijisehemu hutofautiana kati ya tovuti. Watengenezaji wa Wagtail"
" hutumia vijisehemu kwa madhumuni yafuatayo:"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Snippets.md:9
msgid ""
"For blog post authors. As a result, you can add them to multiple pages and "
"manage them from one place. For adverts. This way, you can apply them site-"
"wide or on individual pages. To manage links in a global area of the site. "
"For example, in the footer. For calls to action, such as newsletter sign-up "
"blocks, that may be consistent across many different pages."
msgstr ""
"Kwa waandishi wa machapisho ya blogi. Kwa hivyo, unaweza kuziongeza kwenye "
"kurasa nyingi na kuzidhibiti kutoka sehemu moja. Kwa matangazo. Kwa njia "
"hii, unaweza kuzitumia tovuti nzima au kwenye kurasa za kibinafsi. Ili "
"kudhibiti viungo katika eneo la kimataifa la tovuti. Kwa mfano, katika "
"footer. Kwa wito wa kuchukua hatua, kama vile vizuizi vya kujisajili kwenye "
"jarida, ambavyo vinaweza kuwa sawa katika kurasa nyingi tofauti."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Snippets.md:14
msgid "The Snippets Menu"
msgstr "Menyu ya Vijisehemu"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Snippets.md:16
msgid ""
"You can access the snippets by clicking **Snippets** in the Sidebar. "
"Clicking **Snippets** takes you to the Snippets interface. To add, edit, or "
"delete a snippet, click the snippet type that interests you. Clicking the "
"snippet type takes you to the edit screen, from which you can add, edit, or "
"delete a snippet. Hovering over an individual snippet displays the options "
"to edit or delete that snippet. To add a new snippet to the snippet type, "
"click **Add (snippet type)**."
msgstr ""
"Unaweza kufikia vijisehemu kwa kubofya **Vijisehemu** kwenye Upau wa Kando. "
"Kubofya **Vijisehemu** hukupeleka kwenye kiolesura cha Vijisehemu. Ili "
"kuongeza, kuhariri, au kufuta kijisehemu, bofya aina ya kijisehemu "
"inayokuvutia. Kubofya aina ya kijisehemu kunakupeleka kwenye skrini ya "
"kuhariri, ambayo unaweza kuongeza, kuhariri au kufuta kijisehemu. Kuelea juu"
" ya kijisehemu mahususi huonyesha chaguo za kuhariri au kufuta kijisehemu "
"hicho. Ili kuongeza kijisehemu kipya kwa aina ya kijisehemu, bofya **Ongeza "
"(aina ya kijisehemu)**."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Snippets.md:18
msgid ""
"![Snippet Explorer](../../_static/images/snippets/snippet_explorer.png "
"\"Snippet Explorer\")"
msgstr ""
"![Snippet Explorer](../../_static/images/snippets/snippet_explorer.png "
"\"Snippet Explorer\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Snippets.md:18
msgid "Snippet Explorer"
msgstr "Snippet Explorer"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Snippets.md:20
msgid ""
"Editing a snippet changes it on all of the pages on which it appears. In the"
" top-right corner of the Snippet edit screen, you can see a label saying how"
" many times you have used the snippet. Clicking this label displays a "
"listing of all of these pages."
msgstr ""
"Kuhariri kijisehemu hukibadilisha kwenye kurasa zote ambacho kinaonekana. "
"Katika kona ya juu kulia ya skrini ya kuhariri ya Snippet, unaweza kuona "
"lebo inayosema ni mara ngapi umetumia kijisehemu. Kubofya lebo hii "
"kunaonyesha orodha ya kurasa hizi zote."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Snippets.md:22
msgid "Add snippets while editing a page"
msgstr "Ongeza vijisehemu unapohariri ukurasa"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Snippets.md:24
msgid ""
"Open the Snippets interface in a new tab while editing the page by pressing "
"Ctrl+click in Windows or cmd+click in macOS. You can also open a new tab by "
"right-clicking it and then selecting the Open in new tab option. Add the new"
" snippet from this new tab as you normally would. Then return to your "
"existing tab and reopen the Snippet chooser window by clicking Snippets from"
" the Sidebar."
msgstr ""
"Fungua kiolesura cha Vijisehemu kwenye kichupo kipya wakati wa kuhariri "
"ukurasa kwa kubonyeza Ctrl+bofya kwenye Windows au cmd+bofya kwenye macOS. "
"Unaweza pia kufungua kichupo kipya kwa kubofya kulia na kisha kuchagua "
"Fungua katika kichupo kipya. Ongeza kijisehemu kipya kutoka kwa kichupo hiki"
" kipya kama kawaida. Kisha rudi kwenye kichupo chako kilichopo na ufungue "
"tena dirisha la kuchagua Vijisehemu kwa kubofya Vijisehemu kutoka kwa Upau "
"wa Kando."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Snippets.md:26
msgid ""
"Congratulation, you can now see your new snippet, even though you didn’t "
"leave the edit page."
msgstr ""
"Hongera, sasa unaweza kuona kijisehemu chako kipya, ingawa hukuondoka kwenye"
" ukurasa wa kuhariri."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Snippets.md:28
msgid ""
"Even though this is possible, it is advisable to save your page as a draft "
"as often as possible. This prevents you from accidentally exiting the edit "
"page and losing your changes."
msgstr ""
"Ingawa hili linawezekana, inashauriwa kuhifadhi ukurasa wako kama rasimu "
"mara nyingi iwezekanavyo. Hii hukuzuia kutoka kwa bahati mbaya kwenye "
"ukurasa wa kuhariri na kupoteza mabadiliko yako."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:1
#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:26
#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:61
msgid "Surveys"
msgstr "Tafiti"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:3
msgid "Using Surveys"
msgstr "Kutumia Tafiti"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:5
msgid ""
"Surveys allow you to create a dynamic survey forms, create/modify survey "
"structure, display and analyse survey results and save as PDF Document. With"
" the survey editor it is possible to define conditional logic and answer "
"validation for form fields."
msgstr ""
"Tafiti hukuruhusu kuunda fomu za utafiti zinazobadilika, kuunda/kurekebisha "
"muundo wa utafiti, kuonyesha na kuchanganua matokeo ya uchunguzi na "
"kuhifadhi kama Hati ya PDF. Kwa mhariri wa uchunguzi inawezekana kufafanua "
"mantiki ya masharti na uthibitishaji wa kujibu kwa sehemu za fomu."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:7
msgid ""
"The Survey editor can be accessed from the left side bar under surveys menu."
msgstr ""
"Kihariri cha Utafiti kinaweza kufikiwa kutoka upau wa upande wa kushoto "
"chini ya menyu ya tafiti."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:9
msgid ""
"![Survey Explorer](../../_static/images/surveys/survey_explorer.png \"Survey"
" Explorer\")"
msgstr ""
"![Mtafiti wa Utafiti](../../_static/images/surveys/survey_explorer.png "
"\"Mgunduzi wa Utafiti\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:9
msgid "Survey Explorer"
msgstr "Mchunguzi wa Utafiti"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:11
msgid "Create Surveys and Panel Types"
msgstr "Unda Tafiti na Aina za Paneli"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:13
msgid ""
"To create a survey, you will need to first add a **survey form page**. You "
"can do this by clicking on the **Add survey from page** button at the top "
"right corner of the of the page."
msgstr ""
"Ili kuunda utafiti, utahitaji kwanza kuongeza **ukurasa wa fomu ya "
"uchunguzi**. Unaweza kufanya hivyo kwa kubofya kitufe cha **Ongeza utafiti "
"kutoka kwa ukurasa** kwenye kona ya juu kulia ya ukurasa."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:15
msgid ""
"![Add Survey](../../_static/images/surveys/add_survey_page.png \"Add "
"Survey\")"
msgstr ""
"![Ongeza Utafiti](../../_static/images/surveys/add_survey_page.png \"Ongeza "
"Utafiti\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:15
msgid "Add Survey"
msgstr "Ongeza Utafiti"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:18
msgid ""
"Select a parent page e.g 'Home' and continue to edit the page and supply a "
"Page title. Publish this page. This page will render the form that will be "
"created in the survey creator."
msgstr ""
"Chagua ukurasa mzazi k.m 'Nyumbani' na uendelee kuhariri ukurasa na utoe "
"kichwa cha Ukurasa. Chapisha ukurasa huu. Ukurasa huu utatoa fomu ambayo "
"itaundwa katika mtayarishaji wa utafiti."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:20
msgid ""
"![Survey Parent Page](../../_static/images/surveys/survey_parent.png "
"\"Survey Parent Page\")"
msgstr ""
"![Ukurasa wa Mzazi wa "
"Utafiti](../../_static/images/surveys/survey_parent.png \"Ukurasa wa Mzazi "
"wa Utafiti\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:20
msgid "Survey Parent Page"
msgstr "Utafiti Ukurasa wa Mzazi"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:23
msgid ""
"![Survey Page](../../_static/images/surveys/survey_page.png \"Survey Page\")"
msgstr ""
"![Ukurasa wa Utafiti](../../_static/images/surveys/survey_page.png \"Ukurasa"
" wa Utafiti\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:23
msgid "Survey Page"
msgstr "Ukurasa wa Utafiti"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:26
msgid ""
"Navigate to the Survey creator to create form fields and their logic using "
"the **Survey Creator** button. | "
"![Surveys](../../_static/images/surveys/surveys.png \"Surveys\")"
msgstr ""
"Nenda hadi kwa Muundaji wa Utafiti ili kuunda sehemu za fomu na mantiki yake"
" kwa kutumia kitufe cha **Mtayarishi wa Utafiti**. | "
"![Tafiti](../../_static/images/surveys/surveys.png \"Tafiti\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:31
msgid "The Survey Creator"
msgstr "Muumbaji wa Utafiti"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:33
msgid ""
"This section describes how to perfom basic tasks in the Survey Creator. "
"There are currently two tabs in the creator i.e Designer and Preview tab."
msgstr ""
"Sehemu hii inaeleza jinsi ya kutekeleza majukumu ya msingi katika Muundaji "
"wa Utafiti. Kwa sasa kuna vichupo viwili kwenye kichupo cha Muundaji yaani "
"Mbuni na Onyesho la Kuchungulia."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:35
msgid ""
"![Survey Creator](../../_static/images/surveys/survey_creator.png \"Survey "
"Creator\")"
msgstr ""
"![Mtayarishi wa Utafiti](../../_static/images/surveys/survey_creator.png "
"\"Mtayarishi wa Utafiti\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:35
msgid "Survey Creator"
msgstr "Muumbaji wa Utafiti"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:37
msgid "Designer Tab"
msgstr "Kichupo cha Mbuni"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:39
msgid ""
"By using the Designer tab, you have the ability to customize your survey. "
"You can move questions and panels from the **Toolbox** onto the **Design "
"Surface** through drag and drop, and modify the question, panel, and survey "
"settings using the **Property Grid**."
msgstr ""
"Kwa kutumia kichupo cha Mbuni, una uwezo wa kubinafsisha utafiti wako. "
"Unaweza kuhamisha maswali na vidirisha kutoka **Kikasha** hadi kwenye **Uso "
"wa Muundo** kupitia kuburuta na kuangusha, na kurekebisha swali, paneli, na "
"mipangilio ya uchunguzi kwa kutumia **Gridi ya Mali**."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:41
msgid "Question and Panel Types"
msgstr "Maswali na Aina za Paneli"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "Type"
msgstr "Aina"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "Illustration"
msgstr "Kielelezo"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "<div style=\"width:590px\">Image</div>"
msgstr "<div style=\"width:590px\">Picha</div>"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**Single Input**"
msgstr "**Ingizo Moja**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"For open-ended questions that necessitate brief responses, employ the Single"
" Input type where respondents can input their answers using a single-line "
"text editor."
msgstr ""
"Kwa maswali yasiyo na majibu ambayo yanahitaji majibu mafupi, tumia aina ya "
"Ingizo Moja ambapo wanaojibu wanaweza kuingiza majibu yao kwa kutumia "
"kihariri cha maandishi cha mstari mmoja."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"![Single Input](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-single-input.png"
" \"Single Input\")"
msgstr ""
"![Ingizo Moja](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-single-input.png "
"\"Ingizo Moja\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:46
msgid "Single Input"
msgstr "Ingizo Moja"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**Checkbox**"
msgstr "**kisanduku cha kuteua**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"For questions that allow for multiple answers, utilize the Checkbox type "
"where respondents can choose one or more options by clicking on the "
"corresponding checkboxes."
msgstr ""
"Kwa maswali yanayoruhusu majibu mengi, tumia aina ya kisanduku cha kuteua "
"ambapo wanaojibu wanaweza kuchagua chaguo moja au zaidi kwa kubofya "
"visanduku vya kuteua vinavyolingana."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"![Checkbox](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-checkbox.png "
"\"Checkbox\")"
msgstr ""
"![Kisanduku cha kuteua](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-"
"checkbox.png \"Checkbox\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:47
msgid "Checkbox"
msgstr "Kisanduku cha kuteua"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**Radiogroup**"
msgstr "**Kikundi cha redio**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"For questions that offer several options but allow only one response, use "
"the Radiogroup type where respondents can select a single answer by clicking"
" on one of the radio buttons."
msgstr ""
"Kwa maswali ambayo hutoa chaguo kadhaa lakini huruhusu jibu moja pekee, "
"tumia aina ya Radiogroup ambapo wanaojibu wanaweza kuchagua jibu moja kwa "
"kubofya kwenye moja ya vitufe vya redio."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"![Radiogroup](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-radiogroup.png "
"\"Radiogroup\")"
msgstr ""
"![Rediogroup](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-radiogroup.png "
"\"Radiogroup\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:48
msgid "Radiogroup"
msgstr "Kikundi cha redio"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**Dropdown**"
msgstr "**kunjuzi**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"In the Dropdown type, respondents can choose a single answer from a list of "
"options displayed in a drop-down menu. Similar to Radiogroup, this type is "
"suitable for questions that have multiple options but require only one "
"answer. The Dropdown UI can also show more options while using less screen "
"space."
msgstr ""
"Katika aina ya Kunjuzi, wanaojibu wanaweza kuchagua jibu moja kutoka kwenye "
"orodha ya chaguo zinazoonyeshwa kwenye menyu kunjuzi. Sawa na Radiogroup, "
"aina hii inafaa kwa maswali ambayo yana chaguo nyingi lakini yanahitaji jibu"
" moja tu. Kiolesura cha Kunjuzi kinaweza pia kuonyesha chaguo zaidi huku "
"ukitumia nafasi ndogo ya skrini."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"![Dropdown](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-dropdown.png "
"\"Dropdown\")"
msgstr ""
"![Dropdown](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-dropdown.png "
"\"Dropdown\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:49
msgid "Dropdown"
msgstr "Kunjuzi"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**Comment**"
msgstr "**Maoni**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"For open-ended questions that require respondents to provide lengthy "
"answers, use the Comment type where respondents can input their responses in"
" a resizable multi-line text area. This type is suitable for questions that "
"accept multi-line answers."
msgstr ""
"Kwa maswali ya wazi yanayohitaji wajibu kutoa majibu marefu, tumia aina ya "
"Maoni ambapo wanaojibu wanaweza kuingiza majibu yao katika eneo la maandishi"
" lenye mistari mingi linaloweza kubadilishwa ukubwa. Aina hii inafaa kwa "
"maswali ambayo yanakubali majibu ya mistari mingi."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"![Comment](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-comment.png "
"\"Comment\")"
msgstr ""
"![Maoni](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-comment.png \"Maoni\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:50
msgid "Comment"
msgstr "Maoni"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**Rating**"
msgstr "**Ukadiriaji**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"When you want respondents to provide a rating, use the Rating type where "
"they can select a single number from within a specified range. This type is "
"appropriate for questions that require a rating response."
msgstr ""
"Unapotaka wanaojibu watoe ukadiriaji, tumia aina ya Ukadiriaji ambapo "
"wanaweza kuchagua nambari moja kutoka ndani ya masafa mahususi. Aina hii "
"inafaa kwa maswali yanayohitaji jibu la ukadiriaji."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"![Rating](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-rating.png \"Rating\")"
msgstr ""
"![Ukadiriaji](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-rating.png "
"\"Ukadiriaji\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:51
msgid "Rating"
msgstr "Ukadiriaji"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**Ranking**"
msgstr "**Cheo**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"The Ranking type is suitable for questions where respondents need to "
"establish the order of items. This type allows respondents to drag and drop "
"items from a list to rearrange them based on rank or preference."
msgstr ""
"Aina ya Nafasi inafaa kwa maswali ambapo wahojiwa wanahitaji kuweka "
"mpangilio wa vitu. Aina hii huwaruhusu wanaojibu kuburuta na kuangusha "
"vipengee kutoka kwenye orodha ili kuvipanga upya kulingana na cheo au "
"mapendeleo."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"![Ranking](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-ranking.png "
"\"Ranking\")"
msgstr "![Cheo](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-ranking.png \"Cheo\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:52
msgid "Ranking"
msgstr "Nafasi"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**Image Picker**"
msgstr "**Kiteua Picha**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"In a survey question where respondents are required to select one or several"
" images or videos from a series, a value associated with the chosen image or"
" video is saved to the survey results."
msgstr ""
"Katika swali la utafiti ambapo waliojibu wanatakiwa kuchagua picha au video "
"moja au kadhaa kutoka kwa mfululizo, thamani inayohusishwa na picha au video"
" iliyochaguliwa huhifadhiwa kwenye matokeo ya utafiti."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"![Image Picker](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-imagepicker.png "
"\"Image Picker\")"
msgstr ""
"![Kiteua Picha](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-imagepicker.png "
"\"Kiteua Picha\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:53
msgid "Image Picker"
msgstr "Kiteua Picha"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**Boolean**"
msgstr "**Boolean**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"When using a Boolean editor, respondents can switch between Yes or No to "
"provide their response. The survey results will record the response as true "
"for Yes or false for No."
msgstr ""
"Unapotumia kihariri cha Boolean, wanaojibu wanaweza kubadilisha kati ya "
"Ndiyo au Hapana ili kutoa majibu yao. Matokeo ya utafiti yatarekodi jibu "
"kama kweli kwa Ndiyo au si kweli kwa Hapana."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"![Boolean](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-boolean.png "
"\"Boolean\")"
msgstr ""
"![Boolean](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-boolean.png "
"\"Boolean\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:54
msgid "Boolean"
msgstr "Boolean"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**Signature Pad**"
msgstr "**Pedi ya Sahihi**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"To capture a respondent's signature or any other hand-drawn input, use a "
"type that allows respondents to draw their signature using mouse or touch "
"gestures within a designated input area."
msgstr ""
"Ili kunasa saini ya mjibu aliyejibu au ingizo lingine lolote linalochorwa "
"kwa mkono, tumia aina inayowaruhusu wanaojibu kuchora sahihi zao kwa kutumia"
" ishara za panya au mguso ndani ya eneo lililoteuliwa."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"![Signature Pad](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-signature-"
"pad.png \"Signature Pad\")"
msgstr ""
"![Pedi ya Sahihi](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-signature-"
"pad.png \"Padi ya Sahihi\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:55
msgid "Signature Pad"
msgstr "Pedi ya Sahihi"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**Image**"
msgstr "**Picha**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"The Image type is used to include an image or video in the survey for "
"presentation purposes only. This type does not generate a value to be saved "
"in the survey results."
msgstr ""
"Aina ya Picha inatumika kujumuisha picha au video katika utafiti kwa "
"madhumuni ya uwasilishaji pekee. Aina hii haitoi thamani ya kuhifadhiwa "
"katika matokeo ya utafiti."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**HTML**"
msgstr "**HTML**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"The HTML type can be used to format text, include links, and insert media or"
" custom elements into the survey. This type is solely for presentation "
"purposes and does not produce a value to be saved in the survey results. "
"However, it is important to note that HTML content can be susceptible to "
"security breaches. Therefore, make sure that any links inserted lead to "
"trusted resources."
msgstr ""
"Aina ya HTML inaweza kutumika kutengeneza maandishi, kujumuisha viungo, na "
"kuingiza maudhui au vipengele maalum kwenye utafiti. Aina hii ni kwa "
"madhumuni ya uwasilishaji pekee na haitoi thamani ya kuhifadhiwa katika "
"matokeo ya utafiti. Hata hivyo, ni muhimu kutambua kwamba maudhui ya HTML "
"yanaweza kuathiriwa na ukiukaji wa usalama. Kwa hiyo, hakikisha kwamba "
"viungo vyovyote vilivyowekwa vinaongoza kwenye rasilimali zinazoaminika."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**Expression**"
msgstr "**Maelezo**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The Expression type is used to calculate values and present them to "
"respondents. It can be utilized to sum up scores of previous responses, "
"display current date and time, find an average value, and so on. The "
"calculated value is then saved in the survey results. In the example image "
"provided, the Expression type concatenates the first and last names to "
"display a full name. To define an expression in a survey question, type it "
"into the Expression field found in the General category. Your expression can"
" refer to other survey questions (such as {question1} + {question2}) or use "
"pre-built calculation functions."
msgstr ""
"Aina ya Usemi hutumika kukokotoa thamani na kuziwasilisha kwa wanaojibu. "
"Inaweza kutumika kujumlisha alama za majibu ya awali, kuonyesha tarehe na "
"wakati wa sasa, kupata thamani ya wastani, na kadhalika. Thamani "
"iliyohesabiwa huhifadhiwa katika matokeo ya uchunguzi. Katika picha ya mfano"
" iliyotolewa, aina ya Usemi huunganisha jina la kwanza na la mwisho ili "
"kuonyesha jina kamili. Ili kufafanua usemi katika swali la utafiti, andika "
"katika sehemu ya Usemi unaopatikana katika kitengo cha Jumla. Usemi wako "
"unaweza kurejelea maswali mengine ya utafiti (kama vile {swali1} + {swali2})"
" au kutumia vikokotoa vilivyoundwa awali."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"![Expression](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-expression.png "
"\"Expression\")"
msgstr ""
"![Maelezo](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-expression.png "
"\"Expression\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:58
msgid "Expression"
msgstr "Kujieleza"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**File**"
msgstr "**Faili**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"The File type is used to enable respondents to upload files. They can drag "
"and drop one or several files into the designated area or select files using"
" the browser's Upload File dialog window. Once uploaded, the files are saved"
" in the survey results as base64-encoded strings."
msgstr ""
"Aina ya Faili hutumiwa kuwawezesha wanaojibu kupakia faili. Wanaweza "
"kuburuta na kudondosha faili moja au kadhaa kwenye eneo lililoteuliwa au "
"kuchagua faili kwa kutumia kidirisha cha kidadisi cha Pakia Faili cha "
"kivinjari. Mara baada ya kupakiwa, faili huhifadhiwa katika matokeo ya "
"uchunguzi kama mifuatano ya msingi-64 iliyosimbwa."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "![File](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-file.png \"File\")"
msgstr "![Faili](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-file.png \"Faili\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:59
msgid "File"
msgstr "Faili"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**Single-Choice Matrix**"
msgstr "**Matrix ya Chaguo Moja**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"The Single-Choice Matrix type exhibits radio buttons arranged in rows and "
"columns. Respondents can choose only one radio button within each row."
msgstr ""
"Aina ya Matrix ya Chaguo Moja huonyesha vitufe vya redio vilivyopangwa kwa "
"safu na safu wima. Wanaojibu wanaweza kuchagua kitufe kimoja pekee cha redio"
" ndani ya kila safu mlalo."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"![Single-Choice Matrix](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-matrix-"
"single-choice.png \"Single-Choice Matrix\")"
msgstr ""
"![Matrix ya Chaguo Moja](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-matrix-"
"single-choice.png \"Single-Choice Matrix\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:60
msgid "Single-Choice Matrix"
msgstr "Matrix ya Chaguo Moja"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**Multiple-Choice Matrix**"
msgstr "**Matrix ya Chaguo-Nyingi**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"The Multiple-Choice Matrix type displays rows and columns. Respondents use "
"these editors to select a desired value in each cell. The following image "
"illustrates the Multiple-Choice Matrix type with the default Dropdown "
"editors."
msgstr ""
"Aina ya Matrix ya Chaguo-Nyingi huonyesha safu mlalo na safu wima. Wajibu "
"hutumia vihariri hivi kuchagua thamani inayohitajika katika kila seli. Picha"
" ifuatayo inaonyesha aina ya Multiple-Choice Matrix na vihariri chaguomsingi"
" vya Kunjuzi."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"![Surveys](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-matrix-multiple-"
"choices.png \"Surveys\")"
msgstr ""
"![Tafiti](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-matrix-multiple-"
"choices.png \"Tafiti\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**Dynamic Matrix**"
msgstr "**Dynamic Matrix**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"The Dynamic Matrix type is similar to a [Multiple-Choice "
"Matrix](https://surveyjs.io/survey-creator/documentation/end-user-"
"guide#multiple-choice-matrix), but respondents can add and remove matrix "
"rows."
msgstr ""
"Aina ya Mchanganyiko wa Nguvu ni sawa na [Multiple-Choice "
"Matrix](https://surveyjs.io/survey-creator/documentation/end-user-"
"guide#multiple-choice-matrix), lakini wanaojibu wanaweza kuongeza na kuondoa"
" safu mlalo za matrix."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"![Dynamic Matrix](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-matrix-"
"dynamic-rows.png \"Dynamic Matrix\")"
msgstr ""
"![Dynamic Matrix](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-matrix-"
"dynamic-rows.png \"Dynamic Matrix\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:62
msgid "Dynamic Matrix"
msgstr "Matrix ya Nguvu"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**Multiple Text**"
msgstr "**Maandishi Nyingi**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"Respondents enter their answers into multiple single-line text editors. Use "
"the Multiple Text type for open-ended questions that require more than one "
"short answer."
msgstr ""
"Wajibu huingiza majibu yao katika vihariri vingi vya maandishi ya mstari "
"mmoja. Tumia aina ya Maandishi Nyingi kwa maswali ya wazi yanayohitaji jibu "
"fupi zaidi ya moja."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"![Multiple Text](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-multiple-"
"text.png \"Multiple Text\")"
msgstr ""
"![Maandishi Nyingi](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-multiple-"
"text.png \"Maandishi Nyingi\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:63
msgid "Multiple Text"
msgstr "Maandishi Nyingi"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**Panel**"
msgstr "**Jopo**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"The Panel type is a container for other questions and panels. Use this type "
"to group several questions or panels and control them all together."
msgstr ""
"Aina ya Paneli ni chombo cha maswali na paneli zingine. Tumia aina hii "
"kupanga maswali au paneli kadhaa na uyadhibiti yote kwa pamoja."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid "**Dynamic Panel**"
msgstr "** Paneli Inayobadilika**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"The Dynamic Panel type is a template panel that can contain multiple "
"questions. Respondents can add and remove panels based on the template."
msgstr ""
"Aina ya Paneli Inayobadilika ni kidirisha cha violezo ambacho kinaweza kuwa "
"na maswali mengi. Wanaojibu wanaweza kuongeza na kuondoa vidirisha kulingana"
" na kiolezo."

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md
msgid ""
"![Dynamic Panel](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-dynamic-"
"panel.png \"Dynamic Panel\")"
msgstr ""
"![Dynamic Panel](../../_static/images/surveys/question-types-dynamic-"
"panel.png \"Dynamic Panel\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:65
msgid "Dynamic Panel"
msgstr "Jopo la Nguvu"

#: ../../_docs/manage_content_assets/Manage-Surveys.md:68
msgid "In progress..."
msgstr "Inaendelea..."

