msgid "Content Assets"
msgstr "Vipengee vya Maudhui"

#: ../../_docs/manage_pages/Manage-Flex.md:1
msgid "Flexible Pages (Flex Page)"
msgstr "Kurasa Zinazobadilika (Ukurasa Mwepesi)"

#: ../../_docs/manage_pages/Manage-Flex.md:3
msgid ""
"This is a type of content page that offers a high degree of customization "
"and flexibility in terms of layout and content structure. Unlike other pages"
" above, which have a fixed set of predefined fields, a Flex Page allows you "
"to add various content blocks and sections to create dynamic and richly "
"structured pages."
msgstr ""
"Hii ni aina ya ukurasa wa maudhui ambayo hutoa kiwango cha juu cha "
"kubinafsisha na kubadilika kulingana na mpangilio na muundo wa maudhui. "
"Tofauti na kurasa zingine hapo juu, ambazo zina seti maalum ya sehemu "
"zilizoainishwa awali, Ukurasa wa Flex hukuruhusu kuongeza vizuizi na sehemu "
"mbalimbali za maudhui ili kuunda kurasa zinazobadilika na zenye muundo "
"mzuri."

#: ../../_docs/manage_pages/Manage-Flex.md:5
msgid ""
"With a Flex Page, you have the flexibility to add, rearrange, and customize "
"these content blocks within the page editor. This enables you to build "
"complex and unique page layouts without the need for technical expertise or "
"assistance from developers."
msgstr ""
"Ukiwa na Ukurasa wa Flex, una uwezo wa kuongeza, kupanga upya, na "
"kubinafsisha vizuizi hivi vya maudhui ndani ya kihariri cha ukurasa. Hii "
"hukuwezesha kuunda mipangilio changamano na ya kipekee ya kurasa bila "
"kuhitaji utaalamu wa kiufundi au usaidizi kutoka kwa wasanidi programu."

#: ../../_docs/manage_pages/Manage-Flex.md:7
msgid ""
"The ability to create Flex Pages is one of the features that make Wagtail a "
"powerful and user-friendly ClimWeb. It allows website administrators and "
"editors to have greater control over the presentation of content, making it "
"easier to maintain a consistent design while accommodating diverse content "
"needs across different pages of the website."
msgstr ""
"Uwezo wa kuunda Flex Pages ni mojawapo ya vipengele vinavyofanya Wagtail "
"kuwa ClimWeb yenye nguvu na ifaayo kwa mtumiaji. Huruhusu wasimamizi na "
"wahariri wa tovuti kuwa na udhibiti mkubwa zaidi wa uwasilishaji wa maudhui,"
" na kuifanya iwe rahisi kudumisha muundo thabiti huku ikitosheleza mahitaji "
"mbalimbali ya maudhui katika kurasa tofauti za tovuti."

#: ../../_docs/manage_pages/Manage-Flex.md:11
msgid "Create a Flex Page"
msgstr "Unda Ukurasa wa Flex"

#: ../../_docs/manage_pages/Manage-Flex.md:13
#: ../../_docs/manage_pages/Manage-News.md:37
#: ../../_docs/manage_pages/Manage-Publications.md:40
#: ../../_docs/manage_pages/Manage-Services.md:37
