"To create this page navigate to the 'pages' item on the explorer menu as "
"shown below and click on the pages item at the top."
msgstr ""
"Ili kuunda ukurasa huu nenda kwenye kipengee cha 'kurasa' kwenye menyu ya "
"kichunguzi kama inavyoonyeshwa hapa chini na ubofye kipengee cha kurasa "
"kilicho juu."

