"removed. to access the menu configurations in the ClimWeb, click on the "
"settings and main menu on the left sidebar."
msgstr ""
"Vipengee vya menyu vya urambazaji wa juu wa tovuti vinaweza "
"kuongezwa/kuhaririwa au kuondolewa. kufikia usanidi wa menyu kwenye ClimWeb,"
