"Kulingana na ikiwa ukurasa wa mtoto unaruhusu vipengee vya menyu ndogo au la"
" menyu kunjuzi ya upau wa urambazaji itaonyeshwa. Kila kipengee cha menyu "
"kinachukua:"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Menus.md:12
msgid "link to an internal page / link to a custom URL"
msgstr "kiungo kwa ukurasa wa ndani / kiungo cha URL maalum"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Menus.md:13
msgid "Option to append a value to the url"
msgstr "Chaguo la kuongeza thamani kwenye url"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Menus.md:14
