#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:1
msgid "Users & Roles"
msgstr "Watumiaji & Majukumu"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:3
#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:21
msgid "Manage Users"
msgstr "Dhibiti Watumiaji"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:4
msgid ""
"The ClimWeb allows several users to manage content in the admin interface. "
"These users have roles, which determine the access rights they can exercise."
msgstr ""
"ClimWeb huruhusu watumiaji kadhaa kudhibiti yaliyomo kwenye kiolesura cha "
"msimamizi. Watumiaji hawa wana majukumu, ambayo huamua haki za ufikiaji "
"wanazoweza kutekeleza."

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:6
msgid "By default, there are 5 roles:"
msgstr "Kwa chaguo-msingi, kuna majukumu 5:"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:7
msgid ""
"**Administrator** - This role has complete control over the ClimWeb and can "
"perform tasks such as managing user accounts, creating and deleting pages, "
"and modifying site settings."
msgstr ""
"**Msimamizi** - Jukumu hili lina udhibiti kamili juu ya ClimWeb na linaweza "
"kutekeleza majukumu kama vile kudhibiti akaunti za watumiaji, kuunda na "
"kufuta kurasa, na kurekebisha mipangilio ya tovuti."

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:8
msgid ""
"**Moderator** - A moderator has the next level of access after an "
"administrator. A moderator has access to creating drafts and publishing "
"them."
msgstr ""
"**Msimamizi** - Msimamizi ana kiwango kinachofuata cha ufikiaji baada ya "
"msimamizi. Msimamizi anaweza kufikia kuunda rasimu na kuzichapisha."

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:9
msgid ""
"**Editor** -  This role has the ability to create and edit content on the "
"website. They can add and remove pages, modify existing content, and publish"
" new content."
msgstr ""
"**Mhariri** - Jukumu hili lina uwezo wa kuunda na kuhariri maudhui kwenye "
"tovuti. Wanaweza kuongeza na kuondoa kurasa, kurekebisha maudhui yaliyopo, "
"na kuchapisha maudhui mapya."

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:10
msgid ""
"**Forecaster** - This role provides accurate and timely weather forecasts "
"for the region or area that the website serves."
msgstr ""
"**Mtabiri** - Jukumu hili linatoa utabiri sahihi na kwa wakati unaofaa wa "
"eneo au eneo ambalo tovuti inahudumu."

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:11
msgid ""
"**CAP Composer** - role are authorized to view and create draft CAP alerts, "
"but not to approve nor to publish final CAP alerts;"
msgstr ""
"**Mtunzi wa CAP** - jukumu limeidhinishwa kutazama na kuunda rasimu ya arifa"
" za CAP, lakini sio kuidhinisha au kuchapisha arifa za mwisho za CAP;"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:13
msgid ""
"**CAP Approver** - role are authorized to view and create draft CAP alerts, "
"and approve and publish CAP final alerts"
msgstr ""
"**Midhinishaji wa CAP** - jukumu limeidhinishwa kutazama na kuunda rasimu ya"
" arifa za CAP, na kuidhinisha na kuchapisha arifa za mwisho za CAP"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:15
msgid "Administrator"
msgstr "Msimamizi"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:17
msgid ""
"An administrator has the highest level of access to the admin interface, and"
" are able to perform all actions in the Admin interface. A common task of an"
" administrator is to add, modify, or remove user profiles. As an "
"administrator, you can add, modify, and remove users via the Users "
"interface. To access the Users interface, go to Settings > Users from the "
"Wagtail Sidebar."
msgstr ""
"Msimamizi ana kiwango cha juu zaidi cha ufikiaji wa kiolesura cha msimamizi,"
" na anaweza kufanya vitendo vyote katika kiolesura cha Msimamizi. Kazi ya "
"kawaida ya msimamizi ni kuongeza, kurekebisha, au kuondoa wasifu wa "
"mtumiaji. Kama msimamizi, unaweza kuongeza, kurekebisha, na kuondoa "
"watumiaji kupitia kiolesura cha Watumiaji. Ili kufikia kiolesura cha "
"Watumiaji, nenda kwa Mipangilio > Watumiaji kutoka Upau wa Wagtail."

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:19
msgid ""
"In the Users interface, you can see all of your users, their usernames, "
"roles, and status. The status of a user can either be active or inactive. "
"You can sort this listing either by Name or Username."
msgstr ""
"Katika kiolesura cha Watumiaji, unaweza kuona watumiaji wako wote, majina "
"yao ya watumiaji, majukumu na hali. Hali ya mtumiaji inaweza kuwa hai au "
"isiyotumika. Unaweza kupanga tangazo hili kwa Jina au Jina la Mtumiaji."

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:21
msgid ""
"![Manage Users](../../_static/images/users_and_roles/manage_users.png "
"\"Manage Users\")"
msgstr ""
"![Dhibiti Watumiaji](../../_static/images/users_and_roles/manage_users.png "
"\"Dhibiti Watumiaji\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:23
msgid ""
"You can add a new user, using the 'add a user' button at the top right and "
"assign them an email, username, first name, last name, password and role. "
"Once the ClimWeb user logs in to their account they will be able to edit "
"this information to their preference."
msgstr ""
"Unaweza kuongeza mtumiaji mpya, kwa kutumia kitufe cha 'ongeza mtumiaji' "
"kilicho juu kulia na kumpa barua pepe, jina la mtumiaji, jina la kwanza, "
"jina la mwisho, nenosiri na jukumu. Mtumiaji wa ClimWeb akishaingia kwenye "
"akaunti yake ataweza kuhariri habari hii kwa upendeleo wao."

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:25
msgid ""
"![Add Users](../../_static/images/users_and_roles/add_user.png \"Add "
"Users\")"
msgstr ""
"![Ongeza Watumiaji](../../_static/images/users_and_roles/add_user.png "
"\"Ongeza Watumiaji\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:25
msgid "Add Users"
msgstr "Ongeza Watumiaji"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:27
msgid ""
"Select multiple users by checking the checkbox to the left of each user row,"
" then use the bulk action bar at the bottom to perform an action on all "
"selected users."
msgstr ""
"Chagua watumiaji wengi kwa kuteua kisanduku cha kuteua kilicho upande wa "
"kushoto wa kila safu mlalo ya mtumiaji, kisha utumie upau wa kitendo kikubwa"
" ulio chini ili kutekeleza kitendo kwa watumiaji wote waliochaguliwa."

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:29
msgid ""
"![Select Users](../../_static/images/users_and_roles/select_users.png "
"\"Select Users\")"
msgstr ""
"![Chagua Watumiaji](../../_static/images/users_and_roles/select_users.png "
"\"Chagua Watumiaji\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:29
msgid "Select Users"
msgstr "Chagua Watumiaji"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:31
msgid ""
"Clicking on a user’s name opens their profile in an edit screen. From here, "
"you can then edit that user's details. It is also possible to change users’ "
"passwords from their edit screen, but it is worth encouraging your users to "
"use the Forgotten password link on the login screen instead. This should "
"save you some time!"
msgstr ""
"Kubofya jina la mtumiaji hufungua wasifu wao kwenye skrini ya kuhariri. "
"Kuanzia hapa, unaweza kisha kuhariri maelezo ya mtumiaji huyo. Inawezekana "
"pia kubadilisha manenosiri ya watumiaji kutoka skrini yao ya kuhariri, "
"lakini inafaa kuwahimiza watumiaji wako kutumia kiungo cha Umesahau nenosiri"
" kwenye skrini ya kuingia badala yake. Hii inapaswa kukuokoa muda!"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:33
msgid "Managing Roles"
msgstr "Kusimamia Majukumu"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:35
msgid ""
"To manage (add, edit, delete) roles, select from settings, groups as below. "
"Each group corresponds to a role with permissions."
msgstr ""
"Ili kudhibiti (kuongeza, kuhariri, kufuta) majukumu, chagua kutoka kwa "
"mipangilio, vikundi kama ilivyo hapo chini. Kila kikundi kinalingana na "
"jukumu lililo na ruhusa."

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:37
msgid ""
"![Manage Roles](../../_static/images/users_and_roles/manage_roles.png "
"\"Manage Roles\")"
msgstr ""
"![Dhibiti Majukumu](../../_static/images/users_and_roles/manage_roles.png "
"\"Dhibiti Majukumu\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:37
msgid "Manage Roles"
msgstr "Dhibiti Majukumu"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:39
msgid ""
"![List Roles](../../_static/images/users_and_roles/list_roles.png \"List "
"Roles\")"
msgstr ""
"![Orodhesha Majukumu](../../_static/images/users_and_roles/list_roles.png "
"\"Orodhesha Majukumu\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:39
msgid "List Roles"
msgstr "Orodhesha Majukumu"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:41
msgid ""
"To edit a role and assign different permissions, click on the group. This "
"will navigate to a seperate page where you can manage the permissions of the"
" role."
msgstr ""
"Ili kuhariri jukumu na kukabidhi ruhusa tofauti, bofya kwenye kikundi. Hii "
"itaenda kwenye ukurasa tofauti ambapo unaweza kudhibiti ruhusa za jukumu."

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:43
msgid ""
"![Edit Roles](../../_static/images/users_and_roles/edit_role.png \"Edit "
"Roles\")"
msgstr ""
"![Hariri Majukumu](../../_static/images/users_and_roles/edit_role.png "
"\"Hariri Majukumu\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/Manage-Users-and-Roles.md:43
msgid "Edit Roles"
msgstr "Badilisha Majukumu"

