#: ../../_docs/technical/backup-restore.md:3
msgid "Backup Mechanism"
msgstr "Utaratibu wa Hifadhi nakala"

#: ../../_docs/technical/backup-restore.md:5
msgid ""
"Climweb uses [django-dbbackup](https://github.com/jazzband/django-dbbackup) "
"for backup and restore of the database and media files. The backup process "
"is scheduled using Celery tasks, and currently runs every midnight."
msgstr ""
"Climweb hutumia [django-dbbackup](https://github.com/jazzband/django-"
"dbbackup) kuhifadhi nakala na kurejesha hifadhidata na faili za midia. "
"Mchakato wa kuhifadhi nakala umeratibiwa kwa kutumia kazi za Celery, na kwa "
"sasa unaendeshwa kila usiku wa manane."

#: ../../_docs/technical/backup-restore.md:8
msgid ""
"The https://django-dbbackup.readthedocs.io/en/stable documentation provides "
"detailed information on how the package works."
msgstr ""
"Hati za https://django-dbbackup.readthedocs.io/en/stable hutoa maelezo ya "
"kina kuhusu jinsi kifurushi kinavyofanya kazi."

#: ../../_docs/technical/backup-restore.md:11
msgid "Backup Location"
msgstr "Mahali pa Hifadhi Nakala"

#: ../../_docs/technical/backup-restore.md:13
msgid ""
"Currently, the backup files are store in the local filesystem of the server."
" The location is defined in the settings file as below:"
msgstr ""
"Hivi sasa, faili za chelezo huhifadhiwa katika mfumo wa faili wa ndani wa "
"seva. Eneo limefafanuliwa katika faili ya mipangilio kama ilivyo hapo chini:"

#: ../../_docs/technical/backup-restore.md:23
msgid "DB and Media files restoration"
msgstr "DB na marejesho ya faili za Media"

#: ../../_docs/technical/backup-restore.md:25
msgid "The restore process is done using the `dbrestore` management command."
msgstr ""
"Mchakato wa kurejesha unafanywa kwa kutumia amri ya usimamizi ya "
"`dbrestore`."

#: ../../_docs/technical/backup-restore.md:27
msgid ""
"Ensure you have placed your recent backup files in the backup directory. "
"Usually these are two files, the database dump file and media files tar file"
msgstr ""
"Hakikisha umeweka faili zako za chelezo za hivi majuzi kwenye saraka ya "
"chelezo. Kawaida hizi ni faili mbili, faili ya dampo ya hifadhidata na faili"
" za media tar"

#: ../../_docs/technical/backup-restore.md:30
msgid ""
"You need to start with an empty database with PostGIS as the only external "
"extension installed."
msgstr ""
"Unahitaji kuanza na hifadhidata tupu na PostGIS kama kiendelezi pekee cha "
"nje kilichosakinishwa."

#: ../../_docs/technical/backup-restore.md:32
msgid ""
"If you have extensions like `postgis_topology` or `postgis_tiger_geocoder` "
"installed, you might need to drop these extensions using similar command as "
"below:"
msgstr ""
"Ikiwa una viendelezi kama `postgis_topology` au `postgis_tiger_geocoder` "
"vilivyosakinishwa, unaweza kuhitaji kuangusha viendelezi hivi kwa kutumia "
"amri sawa na hapa chini:"

