msgstr "CMS_SITE_NAME"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"The human-readable name of your Wagtail installation which welcomes users "
"upon login to the Wagtail admin."
msgstr ""
"Jina linaloweza kusomeka na binadamu la usakinishaji wako wa Wagtail ambalo "
