#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "CMS_ADMIN_URL_PATH"
msgstr "CMS_ADMIN_URL_PATH"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"Base Path to admin pages. Do not use `admin` or an easy to guess path. "
"Should be one word and can include an hyphen. DO NOT include any slashes at "
"the start or the end."
msgstr ""
"Njia ya Msingi kwa kurasa za msimamizi. Usitumie `admin` au njia rahisi ya "
"kukisia. Linapaswa kuwa neno moja na linaweza kujumuisha kistari. "
"USIJUMUISHE mikwaju yoyote mwanzoni au mwisho."

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "CMS_DEBUG"
msgstr "CMS_DEBUG"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"A boolean that turns on/off debug mode. Never deploy a site into production "
"with DEBUG turned on"
msgstr ""
"boolean inayowasha/kuzima modi ya utatuzi. Usiwahi kupeleka tovuti katika "
"toleo la umma ukiwa umewasha DEBUG"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
