msgstr "80"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "CMS_BASE_URL"
msgstr "CMS_BASE_URL"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"This is the base URL used by the Wagtail admin site. It is typically used "
"for generating URLs to include in notification emails."
msgstr ""
"Hii ndiyo URL msingi inayotumiwa na tovuti ya msimamizi wa Wagtail. Kwa "
"kawaida hutumiwa kutengeneza URL ili kujumuisha katika barua pepe za arifa."

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "CMS_DEFAULT_LANGUAGE_CODE"
msgstr "CMS_DEFAULT_LANGUAGE_CODE"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"The language code for the CMS. Availabe codes are `en` for English, `fr` "
"from French, `ar` for Arabic, `am` for Amharic, `es` for Spanish, `sw` for "
"Swahili. Default is `en` if not set"
msgstr ""
"Msimbo wa lugha wa CMS. Misimbo inayopatikana ni `en` kwa Kiingereza, `fr` "
"kutoka Kifaransa, `ar` kwa Kiarabu, `am` kwa Kiamhari, `es` kwa Kihispania, "
"`sw` kwa Kiswahili. Chaguo-msingi ni `en` ikiwa haijawekwa"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "en"
msgstr "sw"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "CSRF_TRUSTED_ORIGINS"
msgstr "CSRF_TRUSTED_ORIGINS"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"This variable can be set when CMS_PORT is not 80 e.g if CMS_PORT=8000, "
"CSRF_TRUSTED_ORIGINS would be the following: http://{YOUR_IP_ADDRESS}:8000, "
"http://{YOUR_IP_ADDRESS}, http://localhost:8000 and http://127.0.0.1:8000"
msgstr ""
"Tofauti hii inaweza kuwekwa wakati CMS_PORT si 80 k.m ikiwa CMS_PORT=8000, "
"CSRF_TRUSTED_ORIGINS itakuwa ifuatayo: http://{YOUR_IP_ADDRESS}:8000, "
"http://{YOUR_IP_ADDRESS}, http://localhost:8000 na http://127.80.00:"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "TIME_ZONE"
msgstr "TIME_ZONE"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"A string representing the time zone for this installation. See the [list of "
"time zones](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_tz_database_time_zones). "
"Set this to your country timezone"
msgstr ""
"Mfuatano unaowakilisha saa za eneo za usakinishaji huu. Tazama [orodha ya "
"saa za eneo](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_tz_database_time_zones). "
"Weka hii kwa saa za eneo la nchi yako"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "UTC"
msgstr "UTC"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"[List of tz database time "
"zones](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_tz_database_time_zones)"
msgstr ""
"[Orodha ya saa za maeneo ya hifadhidata ya "
"tz](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_tz_database_time_zones)"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "SECRET_KEY"
msgstr "SECRET_KEY"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"A secret key for a particular Django installation. This is used to provide "
"cryptographic signing, and should be set to a unique, unpredictable value. "
"Django will refuse to start if SECRET_KEY is not set"
msgstr ""
"Kitufe cha siri cha usakinishaji fulani wa Django. Hii inatumika kutoa "
"utiaji sahihi wa kriptografia, na inapaswa kuwekwa kwa thamani ya kipekee, "
"isiyotabirika. Django itakataa kuanza ikiwa SECRET_KEY haijawekwa"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"You can use this online tool [https://djecrety.ir](https://djecrety.ir/) to "
"generate the key and paste"
msgstr ""
"Unaweza kutumia zana hii ya mtandaoni "
"[https://djecrety.ir](https://djecrety.ir/) kutengeneza ufunguo na "
"kubandika."

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "ALLOWED_HOSTS"
msgstr "WENYE_WENYEJI_WANAORUHUSIWA"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"A list of strings representing the host/domain names that this Django site "
"can serve. This is a security measure to prevent HTTP Host header attacks, "
"which are possible even under many seemingly-safe web server configurations."
msgstr ""
"Orodha ya mifuatano inayowakilisha mwenyeji/majina ya vikoa ambayo tovuti "
"hii ya Django inaweza kutumika. Hiki ni hatua ya usalama ili kuzuia "
"mashambulizi ya vichwa vya Seva HTTP, ambayo yanawezekana hata chini ya "
"usanidi mwingi wa seva za wavuti unaoonekana kuwa salama."

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"[Django Allowed "
"Hosts](https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/4.2/ref/settings/#std-setting-"
"ALLOWED_HOSTS)"
msgstr ""
"[Wapangishi Wanaoruhusiwa wa "
"Django](https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/4.2/ref/settings/#std-setting-"
"ALLOWED_HOSTS)"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "SMTP_EMAIL_HOST"
msgstr "SMTP_EMAIL_HOST"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "The host to use for sending email"
msgstr "Mwenyeji wa kutumia kutuma barua pepe"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "SMTP_EMAIL_PORT"
msgstr "SMTP_EMAIL_PORT"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "Port to use for the SMTP server defined in `SMTP_EMAIL_HOST`"
msgstr ""
"Lango la kutumia kwa seva ya SMTP iliyofafanuliwa katika `SMTP_EMAIL_HOST`"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "25"
msgstr "25"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "SMTP_EMAIL_USE_TLS"
msgstr "SMTP_EMAIL_USE_TLS"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"Whether to use a TLS (secure) connection when talking to the SMTP server. "
"This is used for explicit TLS connections, generally on port 587"
msgstr ""
"Iwapo utatumia muunganisho wa TLS (salama) unapozungumza na seva ya SMTP. "
"Hii inatumika kwa miunganisho dhahiri ya TLS, kwa ujumla kwenye bandari 587"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "True"
msgstr "Kweli"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "SMTP_EMAIL_HOST_USER"
msgstr "SMTP_EMAIL_HOST_USER"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"Username to use for the SMTP server defined in `SMTP_EMAIL_HOST`. If empty, "
"Django won’t attempt authentication."
msgstr ""
"Jina la mtumiaji la kutumia kwa seva ya SMTP iliyofafanuliwa katika "
"`SMTP_EMAIL_HOST`. Ikiwa tupu, Django haitajaribu uthibitishaji."

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "SMTP_EMAIL_HOST_PASSWORD"
msgstr "SMTP_EMAIL_HOST_PASSWORD"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"Password to use for the SMTP server defined in `SMTP_EMAIL_HOST`. This "
"setting is used in conjunction with `SMTP_EMAIL_HOST_USER` when "
"authenticating to the SMTP server. If either of these settings is empty, "
"Django won’t attempt authentication."
msgstr ""
"Nenosiri la kutumia kwa seva ya SMTP lililofafanuliwa katika "
"`SMTP_EMAIL_HOST`. Mpangilio huu unatumika pamoja na `SMTP_EMAIL_HOST_USER` "
"wakati wa uthibitishaji kwa seva ya SMTP. Ikiwa mojawapo ya mipangilio hii "
"haina kitu, Django haitajaribu uthibitishaji."

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "CMS_ADMINS"
msgstr "CMS_ADMINS"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"A list of all the people who get code error notifications, in format `\"Name"
" <name@example.com>, Another Name <another@example.com>\"`"
msgstr ""
"Orodha ya watu wote wanaopata arifa za hitilafu za msimbo, katika umbizo "
"`\"Jina <name@example.com>, Jina Jingine <another@example.com>\"`"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "DEFAULT_FROM_EMAIL"
msgstr "DEFAULT_FROM_EMAIL"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"Default email address to use for various automated correspondence from the "
"site manager(s)"
msgstr ""
"Anwani chaguomsingi ya barua pepe ya kutumia kwa mawasiliano mbalimbali ya "
"kiotomatiki kutoka kwa wasimamizi wa tovuti."

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "RECAPTCHA_PUBLIC_KEY"
msgstr "RECAPTCHA_PUBLIC_KEY"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"Google Recaptcha Public Key. https://www.google.com/recaptcha/about/ will "
"need a Google account for RECAPTCHA_PRIVATE_KEY and RECAPTCHA_PUBLIC_KEY "
"creation"
msgstr ""
"Ufunguo wa Umma wa Recaptcha wa Google. "
"https://www.google.com/recaptcha/about/ itahitaji akaunti ya Google ili "
"kuunda RECAPTCHA_PRIVATE_KEY na RECAPTCHA_PUBLIC_KEY"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "RECAPTCHA_PRIVATE_KEY"
msgstr "RECAPTCHA_PRIVATE_KEY"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "Google Recaptcha Private Key"
msgstr "Ufunguo wa Faragha wa Google Recaptcha"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "CMS_NUM_OF_WORKERS"
msgstr "CMS_NUM_OF_WORKERS"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"Gunicorn number of workers. Recommended value should be `(2 x $num_cores) + "
"1 `. For example, if your server has `4 CPU Cores`, this value should be set"
" to `9`, which is the result of `(2 x 4) + 1 = 9`"
msgstr ""
"Idadi ya wafanyakazi wa Gunicorn. Thamani inayopendekezwa inapaswa kuwa `(2 "
"x $num_cores) + 1 `. Kwa mfano, ikiwa seva yako ina `4 CPU Cores`, thamani "
"hii inapaswa kuwekwa kuwa `9`, ambayo ni matokeo ya `(2 x 4) + 1 = 9`"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"[Gunicorn Workers "
"details](https://docs.gunicorn.org/en/latest/design.html#how-many-workers)"
msgstr ""
"[Maelezo ya Wafanyakazi wa "
"Gunicorn](https://docs.gunicorn.org/en/latest/design.html#how-many-workers)"

